<font color="#00ffff">It's a miracle nobody was killed.</font>

08:01.000 --> 08:03.920
<font color="#ffff00">How many living there?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Six families.</font>

08:03.960 --> 08:07.240
<font color="#00ffff">Kenyan Asians.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">The latest only moved in last week.</font>

08:08.360 --> 08:10.360
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing like a warm welcome.</font>

08:26.720 --> 08:27.920
<font color="#00ff00">Morning, sir.</font>

08:31.920 --> 08:36.039
<font color="#ffff00">Let's see. What number was it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">again? </font><font color="#ffffff">4429.</font>

08:36.080 --> 08:40.200
<font color="#ffff00">We're only at 4482 now. He must have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">come in for the last showing.</font>

08:40.240 --> 08:42.640
Was there many in?
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, packed.</font>

08:42.679 --> 08:46.480
<font color="#ffff00">Late night, double feature.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">X certificate. Horror.</font>

08:47.480 --> 08:50.520
<font color="#ffff00">Last night, it was The Pharaoh's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Curse and The Phantom Strangler.</font>

08:50.560 --> 08:52.560
<font color="#00ffff">All all right, Miss Copperstone?</font>

08:52.600 --> 08:54.680
<font color="#ffff00">This gentleman is from the police.</font>

08:54.720 --> 08:56.480
Detective Sergeant Morse.

08:56.520 --> 08:58.440
<font color="#00ffff">Armand De Vere. Manager of the Roxy.</font>

08:58.480 --> 09:01.360
<font color="#00ffff">All's well, I hope?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Just a routine inquiry.</font>

09:01.400 --> 09:02.920
Nothing to be alarmed about.

