<font color="#00ffff">These people are British subjects.</font>

09:44.760 --> 09:47.200
<font color="#00ffff">Passport holders.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We have a responsibility.</font>

09:47.240 --> 09:50.720
<font color="#ffff00">I'm afraid we'll only see more of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it, sir. People whipping up</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ill feeling.</font>

09:50.760 --> 09:53.760
<font color="#00ffff">These "Make Britain Greater" types?</font>

09:53.800 --> 09:56.800
<font color="#00ffff">They put a leaflet through my door</font>
<font color="#00ffff">only the other day:</font>

09:56.840 --> 09:59.320
<font color="#00ffff">"Would you let your daughter marry</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a darkie?"</font>

09:59.360 --> 10:01.160
<font color="#ffff00">Two-bob Blackshirts.</font>

10:01.200 --> 10:03.600
<font color="#00ffff">(INHALES) I thought we'd seen the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">last of them.</font>

10:03.640 --> 10:05.080
<font color="#ffff00">Their sort's always around.</font>

10:05.120 --> 10:08.800
<font color="#ffff00">They find a rock to hide under till</font>
<font color="#ffff00">conditions are right,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and then out they come.</font>

10:08.840 --> 10:11.240
<font color="#00ffff">"The River Tiber foaming with much</font>
<font color="#00ffff">blood."</font>

10:12.240 --> 10:15.640
<font color="#00ffff">Wasn't that it?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The Tiber's not the Isis.</font>

10:15.680 --> 10:17.280
<font color="#00ffff">Hatred is hatred.</font>

10:18.280 --> 10:21.320
<font color="#00ffff">Once that catches hold, there's no</font>
<font color="#00ffff">saying where it might lead.</font>

10:28.280 --> 10:31.200
What's this?
<font color="#00ff00">Emil Valdemar.</font>

10:31.240 --> 10:33.240
<font color="#00ff00">Before your time, I expect.</font>

10:33.280 --> 10:35.560
<font color="#00ff00">One of the big three, he was.</font>

10:35.600 --> 10:38.280
<font color="#00ff00">Karloff and Lugosi at Universal,</font>

10:38.320 --> 10:40.240
<font color="#00ff00">and Valdemar up the road at Mammoth.</font>

10:40.280 --> 10:42.720
And he's coming here, to the Roxy?
<font color="#00ff00">Tomorrow night.</font>

10:42.760 --> 10:45.360
<font color="#00ff00">He's over here shooting a sequel</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to The Pharaoh's Curse.</font>

10:45.400 --> 10:48.320
<font color="#00ff00">He's gonna show clips and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">take questions from the audience.</font>

10:48.360 --> 10:52.120
<font color="#00ff00">Tickets are going like hotcakes.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You gotta get one now,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">if you like horror.</font>

