<font color="#00ffff">MAN: It was only five months.</font>

13:27.200 --> 13:29.640
<font color="#00ff00">Five months?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

13:29.680 --> 13:32.520
<font color="#00ff00">And are you both in full-time</font>
<font color="#00ff00">employment at the moment?</font>

13:32.560 --> 13:34.240
<font color="#ffff00">Hello.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Hello.</font>

13:34.280 --> 13:36.160
<font color="#ffff00">What's your name?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Eisha.</font>

