14:38.120 --> 14:41.760
<font color="#ffff00">If someone had keeled over after</font>
<font color="#ffff00">being in my caff, I might be, too.</font>

14:45.040 --> 14:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">DE VERE: I don't care what you think</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you know or don't know.</font>

14:47.600 --> 14:50.040
<font color="#00ffff">Threaten me and you'll bloody well</font>
<font color="#00ffff">regret it.</font>

