15:19.320 --> 15:21.520
(DIALS NUMBER)

15:22.240 --> 15:23.440
(LINE RINGS)

15:23.480 --> 15:28.040
It's Morse. I'm going off shift as
of 19.31.

15:29.040 --> 15:30.840
Yep. Thank you.

15:35.200 --> 15:38.320
Is everything all right?
<font color="#00ff00">Does it look like it?</font>

15:40.400 --> 15:41.720
<font color="#00ff00">Sorry.</font>

15:41.760 --> 15:44.840
<font color="#00ff00">I was supposed to be meeting</font>
<font color="#00ff00">someone. </font><font color="#ffffff">Ah.</font>

15:46.600 --> 15:49.680
<font color="#00ff00">Where's a good place to get a drink</font>
<font color="#00ff00">round here?</font>

15:49.720 --> 15:51.720
Um...

15:53.400 --> 15:54.800
(CHUCKLES)

15:54.840 --> 15:56.160
Come with me.

15:56.200 --> 15:58.200
I've just finished work.

15:58.240 --> 16:00.240
# BOSSA NOVA JAZZ SONG

16:07.480 --> 16:09.480
<font color="#00ffff">(HUMS ALONG TO SONG)</font>

16:10.720 --> 16:12.240
<font color="#00ffff">(HUMS)</font>

16:15.400 --> 16:17.840
<font color="#00ffff">Morning.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Morning.</font>

16:21.280 --> 16:22.440
<font color="#00ff00">Bye.</font>

16:29.240 --> 16:30.840
(DOOR CLOSES)

16:37.200 --> 16:40.560
<font color="#00ffff">Tea's in the pot.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I think I'll have coffee.</font>

16:40.600 --> 16:42.600
<font color="#00ffff">Suit yourself.</font>

16:44.960 --> 16:46.960
<font color="#00ffff">Who's your friend?</font>

16:47.000 --> 16:48.840
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

16:48.880 --> 16:50.880
She's just some girl.

16:50.920 --> 16:52.920
<font color="#00ffff">I thought you were off the birds.</font>

16:53.840 --> 16:55.840
(PHONE RINGS)

16:59.400 --> 17:01.400
(EXHALES DEEPLY)
<font color="#00ffff">Strange.</font>

17:02.760 --> 17:04.400
<font color="#00ffff">(HANGS UP) Right, look sharp.</font>

17:04.440 --> 17:07.040
<font color="#00ffff">We've an arson on the Watt Court</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Estate.</font>

17:07.079 --> 17:10.079
<font color="#00ffff">Aspirin's in the cabinet.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'll get the car round.</font>

17:12.880 --> 17:14.400
<font color="#00ffff">Petrol through the letterbox.</font>

17:14.440 --> 17:17.040
<font color="#ffff00">Same as the multi-occupancy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on Khartoum Street.</font>

17:19.119 --> 17:20.280
<font color="#00ffff">Aye-aye.</font>

17:27.119 --> 17:29.240
<font color="#00ffff">Hello, stranger.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Jim!</font>

17:30.000 --> 17:33.560
<font color="#00ffff">Long time no see.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Well, you know how it is.</font>

17:33.600 --> 17:36.080
Miss Thursday.
<font color="#00ff00">Morse.</font>

17:37.280 --> 17:38.520
<font color="#00ffff">What's this then, Joanie?</font>

17:39.520 --> 17:42.720
<font color="#00ff00">Um, I've been working here.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Part-time.</font>

17:42.760 --> 17:45.040
Doing what?
<font color="#00ff00">Admin mostly.</font>

17:45.080 --> 17:47.080
<font color="#ffff00">Been any trouble?</font>

17:47.120 --> 17:50.440
<font color="#00ff00">Someone threw a brick at the window</font>
<font color="#00ff00">yesterday. Some yob.</font>

17:50.480 --> 17:53.160
<font color="#00ff00">There was an Asian family in, asking</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for advice.</font>

17:53.200 --> 17:55.560
<font color="#00ffff">Morse. Word through from Dr DeBryn</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on Beavis.</font>

17:55.600 --> 17:58.000
<font color="#00ffff">Says you and the DCI should drop by</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at your earliest.</font>

17:58.040 --> 17:59.400
I'll go get him.

17:59.440 --> 18:02.680
WPC Trewlove will take your statement
when you're ready.

18:26.640 --> 18:28.640
(DOORBELL RINGS)

18:32.280 --> 18:34.640
Good morning. I'm Detective Sergeant
Morse.

18:34.680 --> 18:36.280
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, are you here for Fred?</font>

18:37.720 --> 18:39.720
(DOOR CLOSES)

18:41.840 --> 18:45.080
<font color="#ffff00">Well...who's this, then?</font>

18:45.120 --> 18:48.160
<font color="#00ffff">Morse, he's called.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm Charlie, Fred's brother.</font>

18:48.200 --> 18:52.360
<font color="#ffff00">I see you met my good lady wife,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Paulette. </font><font color="#ffffff">Ah, yes, indeed.</font>

18:52.400 --> 18:55.280
<font color="#ffff00">Well, pull up a seat, son. Take the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">weight off.</font>

18:55.320 --> 19:00.640
<font color="#ffff00">I expect you saw my car, did you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">outside, wonder who it was?</font>

19:00.680 --> 19:03.200
<font color="#ffff00">We're up for the week.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Little break. See the sights.</font>

19:03.240 --> 19:05.080
<font color="#00ffff">It's our first time in Oxford.</font>

19:05.120 --> 19:06.800
Ah.
<font color="#00ff00">Anyone want more tea?</font>

19:06.840 --> 19:11.800
<font color="#ffff00">Oh. Our daughter, Carol.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">This is Fred's boy from work.</font>

19:11.840 --> 19:13.440
<font color="#ffff00">Morse, is it?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

19:13.480 --> 19:16.040
Er... Yes, pleased to meet you.

19:17.920 --> 19:20.440
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe you could find time</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to show her around the place.</font>

19:20.480 --> 19:22.400
<font color="#00ff00">Dad!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Me and Paulette</font>

19:22.440 --> 19:25.240
<font color="#ffff00">are taking Fred and Win out tonight</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for a slap-up meal.</font>

19:25.280 --> 19:28.840
<font color="#ffff00">She won't want to be dragging about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with us old 'uns, will ya?</font>

19:28.880 --> 19:30.760
(APPROACHING FOOTSTEPS)

19:30.800 --> 19:32.240
<font color="#ffff00">Morse.</font>

19:32.280 --> 19:35.320
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, aye-aye, look sharp.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Officer on deck.</font>

19:35.360 --> 19:38.120
Morning, sir.
<font color="#ffff00">Sir, eh? Sir.</font>

19:38.160 --> 19:40.880
<font color="#ffff00">Get you, Fred. Well, how about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that, then? </font><font color="#00ffff">(GIGGLES)</font>

19:40.920 --> 19:42.680
<font color="#ffff00">Arise, Sir Fred.</font>

19:42.720 --> 19:44.720
<font color="#ffff00">Station said something about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">another fire.</font>

19:44.760 --> 19:46.520
Yes, sir.
At the Public Advice Centre.

19:46.560 --> 19:48.000
On Watt Court Estate.

19:48.040 --> 19:50.000
I've left Strange and Fancy to deal.

19:50.040 --> 19:52.920
Dr DeBryn would like to talk to us
about that sudden.

19:52.960 --> 19:55.840
<font color="#00ff00">Public Advice Centre?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Isn't that where Joan's working?</font>

19:55.880 --> 19:59.400
Yes. I've seen her. She's fine.

19:59.440 --> 20:04.320
<font color="#ffff00">I was just asking your lad here if</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he could find time to show</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our Carol round the town.</font>

20:04.360 --> 20:06.760
<font color="#ffff00">I shouldn't think he'll have time,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with his duties.</font>

20:06.800 --> 20:10.080
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you're not at it 24 hours</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a day, surely, eh?</font>

20:10.120 --> 20:12.840
<font color="#ffff00">I wouldn't expect you to pay for it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">out of your own pocket.</font>

20:12.880 --> 20:15.880
That wouldn't be necessary.
<font color="#ffff00">Don't embarrass the man, Charlie.</font>

20:15.920 --> 20:17.840
<font color="#ffff00">You can meet her in town somewhere.</font>

20:17.880 --> 20:20.880
<font color="#ffff00">Take her for a drink,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">say, what, around seven?</font>

20:20.920 --> 20:23.320
<font color="#ffff00">You'd be doing me a favour.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">He doesn't want to.</font>

20:23.360 --> 20:25.880
No, er...

20:25.920 --> 20:27.400
Um...

20:27.440 --> 20:30.240
What about the Sheldonian?

20:30.280 --> 20:31.640
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

20:31.680 --> 20:33.360
<font color="#ffff00">Well, go and put some clothes on.</font>

20:33.400 --> 20:36.840
<font color="#ffff00">Walking round in barely a stitch,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">showing everybody what you've got.</font>

20:36.880 --> 20:40.960
<font color="#00ff00">Dad, you're so embarrassing.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'll see you later. Morse.</font>

20:41.000 --> 20:43.240
<font color="#ffff00">To the Batmobile, eh?</font>

20:45.480 --> 20:50.360
<font color="#00ff00">I have the toxicology report</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on Mr Beavis' blood.</font>

20:50.400 --> 20:52.640
<font color="#00ff00">Nux-vomica.</font>

20:52.680 --> 20:55.080
<font color="#00ff00">Ingested an hour or two before</font>
<font color="#00ff00">his decease.</font>

20:55.120 --> 20:56.320
<font color="#ffff00">Strychnine.</font>

20:56.360 --> 20:59.440
That explains why he didn't eat
what he ordered at the greasy spoon.

20:59.480 --> 21:02.360
<font color="#ffff00">So how did he come by it?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Not at the caff, surely?</font>

21:02.400 --> 21:05.400
<font color="#00ff00">His shirt had one or two spots</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on it.</font>

21:05.440 --> 21:08.640
<font color="#00ff00">Once the lab identified poison,</font>

21:08.680 --> 21:10.680
<font color="#00ff00">I took a swab and tested it.</font>

21:10.720 --> 21:12.520
<font color="#00ff00">It came out positive.</font>

21:12.560 --> 21:16.040
<font color="#00ff00">The poison was in...orange squash.</font>

21:32.160 --> 21:35.680
<font color="#ffff00">Er, I'm afraid Mr De Vere isn't on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">duty yet.</font>

21:35.720 --> 21:39.000
<font color="#ffff00">But I can get the Assistant Manager,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Bullings, for you.</font>

21:39.040 --> 21:40.840
<font color="#ffff00">If you would.</font>

21:43.280 --> 21:45.160
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

21:45.200 --> 21:47.200
<font color="#ffff00">One for the teenagers.</font>

21:47.240 --> 21:51.240
<font color="#ffff00">Emil Valdemar? Must be 80 if he's a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">day. </font><font color="#ffffff">Mm, he's doing some talk here.</font>

21:54.640 --> 21:56.800
<font color="#ffff00">Proper old picture house.</font>

21:56.840 --> 21:58.840
<font color="#ffff00">Don't get many like this anymore.</font>

22:00.120 --> 22:03.800
<font color="#ffff00">We used to go down the Mile End</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Rivoli of a Saturday morning.</font>

22:03.840 --> 22:05.840
<font color="#ffff00">The thrupenny rush.</font>

22:05.880 --> 22:07.200
<font color="#ffff00">(CHUCKLES)</font>

22:07.240 --> 22:10.840
<font color="#ffff00">I'd go in first and spring</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the window in the gents</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for Chas and Billy.</font>

22:10.880 --> 22:14.120
<font color="#ffff00">You ever go?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Where? Saturday morning pictures?</font>

22:15.480 --> 22:17.520
My mother took me once. (Scoffs)

22:17.560 --> 22:20.640
All that screaming in the dark.
It was like something out of Dante.

22:20.680 --> 22:22.440
<font color="#ffff00">(GROANS)</font>

22:22.480 --> 22:24.000
What? I couldn't hear the film.

22:24.040 --> 22:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you don't know what you're</font>
<font color="#ffff00">missing.</font>

22:26.400 --> 22:28.920
<font color="#ffff00">Couple of Maroon Cartoons,</font>

22:28.960 --> 22:30.640
<font color="#ffff00">the serials,</font>

22:30.680 --> 22:32.800
<font color="#ffff00">a Western if you're lucky. Tom Mix.</font>

22:32.840 --> 22:35.920
<font color="#ffff00">Mind you, my favourite was always</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Laurel and Hardy.</font>

22:35.960 --> 22:38.880
<font color="#ffff00">B-I-it me. Bit me.</font>

22:38.920 --> 22:41.440
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

22:41.480 --> 22:43.320
<font color="#ffff00">(SIGHS)</font>

22:43.360 --> 22:45.360
<font color="#ffff00">It's gone now. A buzz bomb got it.</font>

22:48.520 --> 22:52.480
<font color="#ffff00">Look, about Carol. Don't feel you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">have to show her around</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on my account.</font>

22:52.520 --> 22:54.320
Er...

22:54.360 --> 22:56.760
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, back again.</font>

22:56.800 --> 22:58.720
<font color="#00ffff">Molly said something about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the police.</font>

22:58.760 --> 23:00.800
<font color="#ffff00">DCI Thursday, DS Morse,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Thames Valley.</font>

23:00.840 --> 23:04.160
<font color="#ffff00">We're looking into the death</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of one of your patrons.</font>

23:04.200 --> 23:08.040
<font color="#ffff00">Just need to ask a few questions. </font><font color="#00ffff">Of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">course. Anything I can do to help.</font>

23:08.080 --> 23:11.040
These cartons of orange squash.
The Whakahari.

23:11.080 --> 23:14.480
They're sold here and where?
With the usherettes?

23:14.520 --> 23:18.000
<font color="#00ffff">That's right. They load up their</font>
<font color="#00ffff">trays from here or the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">general stores.</font>

23:18.040 --> 23:20.320
So who was on the counter
the night before last?

23:21.280 --> 23:22.680
<font color="#00ffff">That would be me.</font>

23:24.600 --> 23:26.640
Do you remember serving this
customer?

23:26.680 --> 23:29.000
I must warn you,
it's a post-mortem photograph.

23:33.680 --> 23:35.800
<font color="#00ffff">No, I'm afraid not.</font>

23:35.840 --> 23:37.840
<font color="#ffff00">An usherette, perhaps?</font>

23:37.880 --> 23:39.960
<font color="#00ffff">There was only one on.</font>

23:40.000 --> 23:42.480
<font color="#00ffff">Betty. Betty Persky.</font>

23:43.200 --> 23:45.200
(FILM PLAYS)

23:45.240 --> 23:48.520
<font color="#00ff00">Sorry, I don't remember him.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">That's all right, Miss Persky.</font>

23:48.560 --> 23:51.040
<font color="#ffff00">Number of people come through here,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it'd be a miracle</font>

23:51.080 --> 23:52.880
<font color="#ffff00">if you remembered every customer.</font>

23:52.920 --> 23:56.680
<font color="#ffff00">You worked here long?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">A year, just coming up.</font>

23:56.720 --> 23:58.960
<font color="#ffff00">Nice place?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah, it's all right.</font>

23:59.000 --> 24:01.400
<font color="#00ff00">Though I don't know how long</font>
<font color="#00ff00">it'll last.</font>

24:01.440 --> 24:04.760
How's that? <font color="#00ff00">Well, there's talk</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of it being pulled down.</font>

24:04.800 --> 24:06.280
<font color="#00ff00">Flats, I think. Or a car park.</font>

24:06.320 --> 24:09.040
<font color="#ffff00">Where did you hear that?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ssh!</font>

24:09.080 --> 24:10.640
<font color="#00ff00">Off Mr De Vere.</font>

24:10.680 --> 24:13.480
<font color="#00ff00">I was cleaning up behind the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">refreshments,</font>

24:13.520 --> 24:16.840
<font color="#00ff00">when I heard him talking</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to Mr Kegworth, the projectionist.</font>

24:16.880 --> 24:20.280
<font color="#00ff00">I mean, I say talking.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It was more like having words.</font>

24:20.320 --> 24:23.560
MALE VOICE ON SCREEN:
Wilton Road, Oxford. The Taj Mahal.

24:25.240 --> 24:27.680
<font color="#00ffff">I've a friend up at head office.</font>

24:27.720 --> 24:30.720
<font color="#00ffff">He says there's been talk about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">closing the Roxy.</font>

24:30.760 --> 24:33.680
<font color="#00ffff">Some developer looking to buy the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">place.</font>

24:34.560 --> 24:36.600
What did Mr De Vere say?

24:36.640 --> 24:39.120
<font color="#00ffff">That I shouldn't believe all that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I hear.</font>

24:40.520 --> 24:42.480
<font color="#00ffff">The sons want to let it go.</font>

24:42.520 --> 24:46.560
<font color="#00ffff">But Mr Jephson Senior wants to hold</font>
<font color="#00ffff">onto it.</font>

24:46.600 --> 24:49.520
<font color="#ffff00">Be a blow for you, I expect,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if it went.</font>

24:49.560 --> 24:51.560
<font color="#00ffff">They'll all go in the end.</font>

24:52.600 --> 24:54.600
<font color="#00ffff">Well, the television.</font>

24:55.240 --> 24:57.000
<font color="#00ffff">Huh.</font>

24:57.040 --> 24:59.880
<font color="#00ffff">I've been here since it opened.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">40 years near on.</font>

25:00.880 --> 25:03.440
<font color="#00ffff">I've been training my grandson Ken</font>
<font color="#00ffff">up to take over,</font>

25:03.480 --> 25:07.120
<font color="#00ffff">but he seems more drawn to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the, er... the management side.</font>

25:09.400 --> 25:12.360
<font color="#00ffff">When the Roxy goes, I'll go with it.</font>

25:13.960 --> 25:15.480
<font color="#00ffff">And that'll be that.</font>

25:16.520 --> 25:17.920
<font color="#00ffff">Excuse me.</font>

25:23.280 --> 25:25.280
(ORGAN MUSIC)

25:30.040 --> 25:32.680
(SCATTERED APPLAUSE)

25:35.320 --> 25:37.320
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Garnier?</font>

25:37.360 --> 25:40.640
<font color="#00ffff">You've any requests, they'll have to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wait for the next session.</font>

25:40.680 --> 25:44.440
<font color="#ffff00">Police, sir. Detective Chief</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Inspector Thursday,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Detective Sergeant Morse.</font>

25:44.480 --> 25:48.200
<font color="#00ffff">My playing wasn't that bad,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">surely? </font><font color="#ffff00">It sounded very fine, sir.</font>

25:48.240 --> 25:51.560
<font color="#ffff00">No, we're pursuing inquiries</font>
<font color="#ffff00">into a patron of the cinema.</font>

25:51.600 --> 25:54.400
I wonder if you'd take a look at
this photograph.

25:56.120 --> 25:57.960
You've seen him?

25:58.000 --> 25:59.800
<font color="#00ffff">Night before last.</font>

25:59.840 --> 26:03.120
<font color="#00ffff">Between the intermission and the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Queen,</font>

26:03.160 --> 26:05.480
<font color="#00ffff">I've usually a couple of hours</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on my hands.</font>

26:05.520 --> 26:10.120
<font color="#00ffff">I'll have a smoke,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">maybe take a look at the paper.</font>

26:11.120 --> 26:14.840
<font color="#00ffff">Normally, nobody's in here</font>
<font color="#00ffff">when the picture's showing.</font>

26:14.880 --> 26:19.720
<font color="#00ffff">Only, this time...there he was.</font>

26:19.760 --> 26:21.160
<font color="#00ffff">Your man Beavis.</font>

26:21.200 --> 26:24.480
What was he doing?
<font color="#00ffff">Just standing there.</font>

26:25.480 --> 26:27.280
<font color="#00ffff">Waiting, I'd have said.</font>

26:27.320 --> 26:32.920
<font color="#00ffff">I asked him his business, and he</font>
<font color="#00ffff">said he was looking for the gents.</font>

26:32.960 --> 26:36.080
<font color="#00ffff">So I told him where it was,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and he went on his way.</font>

26:36.120 --> 26:39.040
<font color="#ffff00">And that was it, was it?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

26:39.080 --> 26:44.560
<font color="#00ffff">Normally, I'd have forgotten all</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about it, if that's all it was.</font>

26:45.640 --> 26:49.760
<font color="#00ffff">But sometimes, when it's a clear</font>
<font color="#00ffff">night,</font>

26:49.800 --> 26:52.160
<font color="#00ffff">I'll go up onto the roof.</font>

26:52.200 --> 26:55.000
<font color="#00ffff">Oxford by moonlight.</font>

26:55.040 --> 26:58.560
<font color="#00ffff">Just you and the stars.</font>

26:58.600 --> 27:00.560
<font color="#00ffff">I heard someone talking,</font>

27:00.600 --> 27:02.600
<font color="#00ffff">so I wandered over to the edge.</font>

27:02.640 --> 27:05.520
<font color="#00ffff">And he was on the fire escape</font>
<font color="#00ffff">landing,</font>

27:05.560 --> 27:08.800
<font color="#00ffff">talking to someone by the Circle</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fire exit.</font>

27:18.280 --> 27:20.720
<font color="#ffff00">And you couldn't see who it was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he was talking to?</font>

27:20.760 --> 27:22.160
<font color="#00ffff">No, they never came out.</font>

27:22.200 --> 27:24.480
<font color="#00ffff">Then the door shut, and he went on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his way.</font>

27:24.520 --> 27:27.080
<font color="#00ffff">I stubbed my smoke and went back</font>
<font color="#00ffff">down.</font>

27:41.000 --> 27:45.080
<font color="#00ff00">Hard to see how someone could have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">got the poison inside if</font>
<font color="#00ff00">it was sealed.</font>

27:45.120 --> 27:47.200
<font color="#00ff00">Nobody will drink from a carton</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that's open.</font>

27:47.240 --> 27:50.600
<font color="#00ffff">Depends if Beavis was the intended</font>
<font color="#00ffff">victim or we've a madman on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">our hands.</font>

27:50.640 --> 27:53.920
<font color="#00ff00">Could have been poisoned at random,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you think? Just a face in the crowd?</font>

27:53.960 --> 27:57.320
The organist was under the impression
he was meeting someone at the Roxy.

27:57.360 --> 28:00.840
Maybe another patron or a member of
staff. Which would suggest
it was meant.

28:00.880 --> 28:02.960
<font color="#00ff00">He was a retired Detective Sergeant.</font>

28:03.000 --> 28:05.760
<font color="#00ff00">One of his old cases, you think?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Someone with a grudge?</font>

28:05.800 --> 28:09.040
<font color="#00ffff">Nine years retired, sir.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Late in the day for revenge.</font>

28:09.080 --> 28:12.600
<font color="#ffff00">That's one thing it's never too late</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for. Start going through his</font>
<font color="#ffff00">old cases.</font>

28:12.640 --> 28:15.360
<font color="#ffff00">See if he's ever nicked anyone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">who works at the cinema.</font>

28:15.400 --> 28:18.280
<font color="#00ffff">Unless he bought his orange squash</font>
<font color="#00ffff">somewhere else.</font>

28:20.000 --> 28:22.640
That's unlikely, I'd have thought.

28:22.680 --> 28:26.680
<font color="#ffff00">But not impossible. Trace all the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">routes he could have taken</font>
<font color="#ffff00">between the two.</font>

28:26.720 --> 28:29.360
<font color="#ffff00">Show his picture at any pub</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you find along the way.</font>

28:29.400 --> 28:33.400
<font color="#00ff00">What do we know about the cinema?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Not much, sir. Owned by the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Jephsons.</font>

28:33.440 --> 28:35.560
<font color="#ffff00">There was talk of a sale</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for redevelopment,</font>

28:35.600 --> 28:37.560
<font color="#ffff00">but I can't see Beavis might</font>
<font color="#ffff00">figure in it.</font>

28:37.600 --> 28:39.120
<font color="#00ff00">Right, well, keep me informed.</font>

28:39.160 --> 28:42.480
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, anything more on these arson</font>
<font color="#00ff00">cases? </font><font color="#00ffff">Matter of fact, sir,</font>

28:42.520 --> 28:46.080
<font color="#00ffff">I've heard back on the owner of the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Advice Centre. Another one</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Eddie Nero's.</font>

28:46.120 --> 28:48.760
<font color="#00ff00">The proverbial bad penny.</font>

28:48.800 --> 28:52.120
<font color="#00ff00">Nobody thought to burn down</font>
<font color="#00ff00">his wretched gym, I suppose.</font>

28:52.160 --> 28:53.960
<font color="#00ff00">Well, carry on.</font>

28:54.840 --> 28:57.200
(BIRDSONG)

29:03.200 --> 29:06.120
<font color="#ffff00">You know, you shouldn't be too hard</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on the boy.</font>

29:06.160 --> 29:07.600
<font color="#ffff00">It's encouragement he wants.</font>

29:07.640 --> 29:10.520
<font color="#ffff00">A bit of praise goes a long way.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Checking local boozers?</font>

29:10.560 --> 29:12.600
That's not police work, that's a pub
crawl.

29:12.640 --> 29:15.560
He comes back with anything more
than a skinful, I'll eat my hat.

29:15.600 --> 29:18.840
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe it's a 20-1 shot, but I gave</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you a long lead often enough.</font>

29:18.880 --> 29:20.560
<font color="#ffff00">Some of the schemes you come up</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with.</font>

29:20.600 --> 29:22.920
But I knew what I was doing.
<font color="#ffff00">Not always.</font>

29:22.960 --> 29:25.280
<font color="#ffff00">But often enough to make a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">difference.</font>

29:25.320 --> 29:27.520
<font color="#ffff00">Give him a chance.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">He might surprise you.</font>

29:41.160 --> 29:43.160
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

29:43.760 --> 29:47.760
<font color="#00ff00">As I told your colleague,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">he worked as a nightwatchman.</font>

29:47.800 --> 29:51.280
<font color="#00ff00">Lately, he'd been filling in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for an attendant who's off sick.</font>

29:52.480 --> 29:54.600
Did he ever mention the Roxy cinema
to you?

29:54.640 --> 29:56.520
A member of staff that he knew,
maybe?

29:56.560 --> 30:00.160
<font color="#00ff00">Not to me. But I did not know him</font>
<font color="#00ff00">particularly well.</font>

30:00.200 --> 30:02.440
<font color="#00ff00">I am on loan from the Cairo Museum.</font>

30:02.480 --> 30:05.000
<font color="#00ff00">Together with some of the visiting</font>
<font color="#00ff00">exhibits.</font>

30:05.040 --> 30:08.400
<font color="#ffff00">So you mind all the bits and pieces</font>
<font color="#ffff00">down here?</font>

30:08.440 --> 30:10.720
<font color="#00ff00">(CHUCKLES) If by that you mean</font>

30:10.760 --> 30:16.120
<font color="#00ff00">do I make sure no harm befalls the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">priceless artefacts of my people's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ancient history,</font>

30:16.160 --> 30:18.520
<font color="#00ff00">then yes, I mind the bits</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and pieces.</font>

30:18.560 --> 30:21.160
<font color="#ffff00">No slight was intended, Doctor.</font>

30:22.160 --> 30:24.640
<font color="#00ff00">With the British, it never is.</font>

30:24.680 --> 30:27.320
<font color="#00ff00">And yet, as I say, I hardly knew</font>
<font color="#00ff00">him.</font>

30:27.360 --> 30:29.440
<font color="#00ff00">There is nothing more</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I can tell you.</font>

30:30.440 --> 30:32.240
<font color="#00ff00">If you'll excuse me, I have much to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">do.</font>

30:38.800 --> 30:41.280
<font color="#ffff00">He doesn't seem to have been close</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to anyone at work</font>

30:41.320 --> 30:44.760
<font color="#ffff00">but, having met his supervisor, a Dr</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Shoukry, I can't say as I blame him.</font>

30:44.800 --> 30:47.000
<font color="#ffff00">Not what you'd call a sunny</font>
<font color="#ffff00">personality, sir.</font>

30:47.040 --> 30:49.640
<font color="#ffff00">And none too keen on the British,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">by the sound of things.</font>

30:49.680 --> 30:51.440
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah, well, we've all met that type.</font>

30:51.480 --> 30:53.240
<font color="#00ffff">Chip on the shoulder a mile wide.</font>

30:53.280 --> 30:56.160
<font color="#00ffff">They want to remember who it was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">built the bloody Suez Canal.</font>

30:56.200 --> 30:59.400
It was the French.
<font color="#00ffff">Was it?</font>

31:00.560 --> 31:03.960
<font color="#ffff00">Any event, working nights</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he mostly brought in his own snaps.</font>

31:04.000 --> 31:07.920
<font color="#ffff00">That still leaves only the cinema or</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the caff where he'd come by</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this poisoned squash.</font>

31:07.960 --> 31:09.720
<font color="#00ff00">Or a public house, of course.</font>

31:09.760 --> 31:12.440
Oh, yes. Any luck with that,
Constable?

31:14.080 --> 31:18.040
<font color="#00ffff">No. Nobody's...nobody's seen him.</font>

31:18.080 --> 31:22.360
<font color="#00ff00">No, well, Morse thought it unlikely.</font>

31:22.400 --> 31:24.720
<font color="#00ffff">(HICCUPS)</font>

31:24.760 --> 31:26.800
Cold water's good for hiccups.

31:26.840 --> 31:30.640
<font color="#ffff00">Er, one or two, er...other matters</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to go over, sir, if you've a moment.</font>

31:30.680 --> 31:32.680
<font color="#00ff00">Yes. Yes, of course.</font>

31:33.720 --> 31:35.880
(EXHALES)
<font color="#00ffff">(CONSTABLE FANCY HICCUPS)</font>

31:39.400 --> 31:42.120
Don't ever come in here half-cut
again. Do you understand?

31:42.160 --> 31:44.160
This isn't a game.

31:45.120 --> 31:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">STRANGE: All done?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">For now.</font>

31:47.600 --> 31:49.680
<font color="#00ffff">Got a nice bit of haddock</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for tonight.</font>

31:49.720 --> 31:52.400
<font color="#00ffff">Thought I might do it with a poached</font>
<font color="#00ffff">egg. Bit of pepper.</font>

31:52.440 --> 31:53.760
<font color="#00ffff">Bread and scrape.</font>

31:55.600 --> 31:58.320
MORSE: Well, I can't.
I've got a date.

32:08.200 --> 32:10.120
<font color="#ffff00">I wondered if I had the right place.</font>

32:10.160 --> 32:12.840
<font color="#ffff00">Everyone said this was it.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I was held up at work.</font>

32:12.880 --> 32:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">I wasn't complaining.</font>

32:14.200 --> 32:16.000
<font color="#ffff00">A civil servant?</font>

32:16.040 --> 32:18.960
You tell some people you're a police
officer and they run a mile.

32:19.000 --> 32:21.080
You weren't exactly forthcoming
yourself.

32:21.120 --> 32:23.240
<font color="#ffff00">I remember there wasn't much</font>
<font color="#ffff00">talking at all.</font>

32:23.280 --> 32:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">If I've put you on the spot, they</font>
<font color="#ffff00">think I stayed at Cousin Joan's.</font>

32:26.400 --> 32:28.760
What did she think?
<font color="#ffff00">She didn't think anything.</font>

32:28.800 --> 32:31.880
<font color="#ffff00">That's who I was supposed to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">seeing. Only, she was busy.</font>

32:33.200 --> 32:34.480
<font color="#ffff00">Fate.</font>

32:34.520 --> 32:35.840
Look... (SIGHS)

32:35.880 --> 32:39.560
The thing about mistakes is not to
repeat them.

32:41.240 --> 32:43.680
<font color="#ffff00">Is that what it was? A mistake?</font>

32:43.720 --> 32:46.160
<font color="#ffff00">It's not like anyone got hurt,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is it?</font>

32:47.480 --> 32:49.480
What would you like to see first?

32:49.520 --> 32:51.600
<font color="#ffff00">It's up to you.</font>

32:51.640 --> 32:54.480
Well, this is as good a place to
start as any.

32:55.600 --> 32:59.760
Sheldonian Theatre. Built after
the Restoration by Christopher Wren.

32:59.800 --> 33:03.920
Named for the Chancellor of the
university at the time:
Gilbert Sheldon.

33:03.960 --> 33:05.960
Shall we?

33:07.480 --> 33:12.480
<font color="#00ff00">Well, this is very nice, I must say.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Best in town. I made sure of it.</font>

33:12.520 --> 33:15.240
<font color="#ffff00">Order anything you like.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Tonight's on me.</font>

33:15.280 --> 33:18.200
No need to push the boat out,
Charlie. Not on our account.

33:18.240 --> 33:20.200
<font color="#ffff00">Let me worry about that.</font>

33:20.240 --> 33:22.080
<font color="#00ffff">Ooh, it's a big menu.</font>

33:22.120 --> 33:26.600
<font color="#ffff00">Course it's a big menu. It's not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sammy's Pie and Mash shop, is it?</font>

33:26.640 --> 33:29.760
<font color="#00ffff">(LAUGHS) </font><font color="#ffff00">Come on, let's have some</font>
<font color="#ffff00">service here, John.</font>

33:31.200 --> 33:34.240
<font color="#ffff00">My mouth is as dry as Geronimo's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">sock.</font>

33:35.120 --> 33:38.320
And through here is the Radcliffe
Camera.

33:38.360 --> 33:39.760
<font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font>

33:42.720 --> 33:44.720
(BELL CHIMES)

33:45.800 --> 33:47.600
And this is Hertford Bridge.

33:47.640 --> 33:50.880
Most people call it The Bridge of
Sighs after its namesake in Venice.

33:50.920 --> 33:53.640
But it more closely resembles the
Rialto Bridge.

33:53.680 --> 33:55.560
<font color="#ffff00">It's lovely.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mm.</font>

33:55.600 --> 33:57.080
(BICYCLE BELL TINKLES)

33:57.120 --> 33:59.120
Come on. The Ashmolean.

34:01.440 --> 34:03.440
What? What is it?

34:04.560 --> 34:07.200
<font color="#ffff00">Look, I can just get the bus back,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if you tell me which one.</font>

34:07.240 --> 34:10.719
<font color="#ffff00">And I won't say anything to Uncle</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Fred. </font><font color="#ffffff">No, it's not that.</font>

34:10.760 --> 34:12.000
(SIGHS)

34:12.040 --> 34:13.679
I'm sorry.

34:15.560 --> 34:17.239
What would you like to do?

34:20.560 --> 34:22.080
(CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING)

34:37.480 --> 34:40.000
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Xarkoff. Armand De Vere,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the manager.</font>

34:40.040 --> 34:44.320
<font color="#00ffff">May I welcome you on behalf of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Jephson Cinemas to the Roxy.</font>

34:44.360 --> 34:45.840
<font color="#00ff00">Happy to be here.</font>

34:45.880 --> 34:49.679
<font color="#00ff00">May I present Miss Veronique</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Carlton, our leading lady.</font>

34:49.719 --> 34:51.400
<font color="#ffff00">Charmed.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">(CLICKS FINGERS)</font>

34:51.440 --> 34:54.199
<font color="#00ffff">Wonderful to meet you, Miss Carlton.</font>

34:55.320 --> 34:58.360
<font color="#00ff00">Is Emil here yet?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">He arrived about half an hour ago,</font>

34:58.400 --> 35:01.240
<font color="#00ffff">but he was feeling a bit tired</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so I've let him use my flat.</font>

35:01.280 --> 35:02.520
<font color="#00ffff">Er, apartment.</font>

35:02.560 --> 35:05.880
<font color="#00ff00">And Jason?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Running a little late.</font>

35:07.040 --> 35:08.320
<font color="#00ffff">Shall we?</font>

35:11.160 --> 35:12.520
(DOOR OPENS)

35:14.200 --> 35:15.680
(DOOR CLOSES)

35:15.720 --> 35:19.320
<font color="#ffff00">Someone looks as though they've lost</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a shilling and found sixpence.</font>

35:19.360 --> 35:20.840
<font color="#00ffff">Don't you start.</font>

35:20.880 --> 35:22.120
<font color="#ffff00">Why? What's up?</font>

35:24.160 --> 35:27.240
<font color="#00ffff">I'm in the doghouse, aren't I?</font>

35:30.880 --> 35:34.040
<font color="#ffff00">Are you sure we're allowed in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here? </font><font color="#ffffff">I'm a policeman.</font>

35:34.080 --> 35:36.200
I'm allowed anywhere.

35:36.240 --> 35:38.560
<font color="#00ffff">Another drink for Mr Nero, please,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Betty.</font>

35:42.920 --> 35:44.120
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, my God.</font>

35:45.200 --> 35:46.480
<font color="#ffff00">It's Jason Curwen!</font>

35:46.520 --> 35:48.560
Who?

35:48.600 --> 35:51.960
<font color="#ffff00">The blind violinist in Two Weeks</font>
<font color="#ffff00">In August.</font>

35:52.000 --> 35:53.720
<font color="#ffff00">With Diana Day!</font>

35:55.440 --> 36:00.720
What would you like to drink?
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, I don't mind. You choose.</font>

36:03.600 --> 36:05.080
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, sir. What can I get for you?</font>

36:05.120 --> 36:08.840
Could I have a champagne and a
scotch. Thank you.

36:08.880 --> 36:10.880
<font color="#ffff00">Not over there, OK?</font>

36:18.600 --> 36:20.880
That's all very well, Professor,
but you realise

36:20.920 --> 36:25.680
every last member of the original
expedition died in highly unusual
circumstances.

36:25.720 --> 36:29.240
All except...yourself.

36:30.080 --> 36:32.560
<font color="#00ffff">As may be, Steven,</font>

36:32.600 --> 36:34.920
<font color="#00ffff">but what you're suggesting</font>

36:34.960 --> 36:39.320
<font color="#00ffff">breaks all the natural laws of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">science known to man.</font>

36:41.040 --> 36:45.720
<font color="#00ffff">A creature restored to life after</font>
<font color="#00ffff">three-and-a-half thousand years?</font>

36:45.760 --> 36:48.120
<font color="#00ffff">And hell-bent on revenge?</font>

36:48.880 --> 36:50.680
<font color="#00ffff">Impossible!</font>

36:53.280 --> 36:54.880
Excuse me.

36:55.600 --> 36:57.720
(DRAMATIC MUSIC)

37:13.160 --> 37:15.280
<font color="#00ff00">(GROWLS)</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(AUDIENCE GASPS)</font>

37:15.320 --> 37:16.960
<font color="#00ff00">(GRUNTS)</font>

37:17.960 --> 37:20.760
(DOOR CREAKS)

37:27.320 --> 37:29.320
<font color="#00ffff">DE VERE: You simply can't do that!</font>

37:29.360 --> 37:32.440
<font color="#ffff00">No ifs, no buts. It's happening.</font>

37:32.480 --> 37:35.480
<font color="#00ffff">But, Mr Nero, please!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Enough! Go on.</font>

37:44.200 --> 37:47.320
<font color="#ffff00">(SCREAMS)</font>

37:47.360 --> 37:51.280
<font color="#00ffff">Oh! Oh! Oh! Argh!</font>

37:51.320 --> 37:53.320
<font color="#ffff00">(WOMAN SCREAMS)</font>

37:57.640 --> 37:59.720
<font color="#00ff00">(GRUNTS)</font>

37:59.760 --> 38:01.760
<font color="#ffff00">(WOMAN SCREAMS)</font>

38:03.760 --> 38:05.040
<font color="#00ff00">(MUTTERS INCOHERENTLY)</font>

38:05.080 --> 38:07.200
<font color="#00ffff">(SCREAMS)</font>

38:07.240 --> 38:08.400
Victoria!

38:08.880 --> 38:10.880
Steven!

38:17.240 --> 38:19.280
<font color="#00ff00">Come to me.</font>

38:34.640 --> 38:36.640
<font color="#ffff00">(CHARLIE CHUCKLES)</font>

38:57.440 --> 39:01.800
<font color="#00ffff">Ladies and gentlemen, a sneak</font>
<font color="#00ffff">preview of some marvellous clips</font>

39:01.840 --> 39:05.200
<font color="#00ffff">of Zoltan Xarkoff's latest</font>
<font color="#00ffff">production, The Pharaoh Rises.</font>

39:05.240 --> 39:07.120
I must protest!

39:07.160 --> 39:11.680
This fantasy is grossly disrespectful
to the culture of the Egyptians!

39:11.720 --> 39:14.520
<font color="#00ff00">Please sit down, sir! </font><font color="#ffffff">Bad enough our</font>
<font color="#ffffff">treasures have for centuries</font>

39:14.560 --> 39:15.960
been plundered by Europeans.

39:16.000 --> 39:19.400
But this latest affront... <font color="#00ffff">With</font>
<font color="#00ffff">respect, sir, it's an entertainment.</font>

39:19.440 --> 39:22.440
To you, perhaps. Not for us. Not for
us.

39:22.480 --> 39:24.200
<font color="#00ff00">Come along now, sir.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I warn you,</font>

39:24.240 --> 39:25.600
<font color="#00ff00">all of you,</font>

39:25.640 --> 39:28.760
<font color="#00ff00">if you persist with this sacrilege,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you will answer for it!</font>

39:28.800 --> 39:31.040
<font color="#00ffff">Apologies, ladies and gentlemen.</font>

39:32.040 --> 39:35.040
<font color="#00ffff">Well, what can one say about the man</font>
<font color="#00ffff">we are to honour tonight?</font>

39:35.080 --> 39:37.080
<font color="#00ffff">Decorated war hero,</font>

39:37.120 --> 39:39.520
<font color="#00ffff">star of the early silent films,</font>

39:39.560 --> 39:42.560
<font color="#00ffff">alongside Pickford, Chaplin and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Fairbanks.</font>

39:42.600 --> 39:46.280
<font color="#00ffff">And then the work for which he is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">justly famous:</font>

39:46.320 --> 39:52.200
<font color="#00ffff">a classic series of horror films</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at Mammoth Pictures Studios.</font>

39:52.240 --> 39:56.920
<font color="#00ffff">Ladies and gentlemen, it is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a great honour to introduce</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Emil Valdemar, MC.</font>

40:03.160 --> 40:05.440
You're very kind. Thank you.

40:06.720 --> 40:08.960
<font color="#00ff00">Well, that was lovely.</font>

40:09.000 --> 40:13.160
<font color="#ffff00">Do you want more splosh, Win? </font><font color="#00ff00">Not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">too much, Charlie.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You'll have me tiddly.</font>

40:14.800 --> 40:19.440
<font color="#00ff00">Dad, where's the er...? </font><font color="#ffffff">It's just on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the right, where we came in.</font>

40:19.480 --> 40:23.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'll keep you company. I'm bursting.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

40:32.200 --> 40:35.480
<font color="#ffff00">Good to see you, Fred.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You too, Charlie.</font>

40:36.880 --> 40:39.920
You're looking well. How's business
your end?

40:39.960 --> 40:43.560
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you know, funny you should</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ask, Fred.</font>

40:43.600 --> 40:47.800
<font color="#ffff00">I'd like your advice on a little</font>
<font color="#ffff00">thing that's, er...come up.</font>

40:47.840 --> 40:52.280
<font color="#ffff00">But not here, eh? We'll talk about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it amongst ourselves, without</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the girls.</font>

40:52.320 --> 40:55.920
Of course. Nothing serious though,
is it?

40:55.960 --> 40:58.920
<font color="#ffff00">No, no, no. Never better.</font>

41:00.120 --> 41:01.720
<font color="#00ff00">Thursday.</font>

41:05.680 --> 41:08.520
<font color="#ffff00">Friend of yours, Fred?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Evening, sir.</font>

41:08.560 --> 41:11.520
<font color="#00ff00">I had no idea you were an habitue</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of Chez Andre. Please sit down.</font>

41:11.560 --> 41:14.640
Oh, I'm not, er, usually, sir.

41:14.680 --> 41:18.160
My middle brother, Charlie,
Chief Superintendent Bright.

41:18.200 --> 41:21.120
<font color="#ffff00">Bit of a mouthful.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What do they call you at home?</font>

41:21.160 --> 41:22.440
<font color="#00ff00">Reginald.</font>

41:22.480 --> 41:24.440
<font color="#ffff00">Pull up a chair, join us</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for a nightcap.</font>

41:24.480 --> 41:27.800
<font color="#00ff00">No, no, really, I wouldn't wish to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">intrude on a family occasion.</font>

41:27.840 --> 41:30.240
<font color="#ffff00">The more the merrier. I insist.</font>

41:30.280 --> 41:32.840
<font color="#00ff00">That's very kind of you.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Thank you. </font><font color="#ffff00">(CLICKS FINGERS) Hey!</font>

41:32.880 --> 41:34.680
<font color="#ffff00">Another chair for our guest.</font>

41:34.720 --> 41:37.440
<font color="#ffff00">Erm, what can I get you, Reg?</font>

41:37.480 --> 41:41.040
<font color="#00ff00">Reginald. I'll have a brandy,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I think, if I may.</font>

41:41.080 --> 41:45.760
Talking about all these old movies
makes me wonder if I really did
all that.

41:45.800 --> 41:48.960
(LAUGHTER)
<font color="#00ffff">Well, you did. And more.</font>

41:49.000 --> 41:51.120
<font color="#00ffff">And now, of course, The Pharaoh</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Rises,</font>

41:51.160 --> 41:55.000
<font color="#00ffff">in which you play not only the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">eponymous hero,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but also his nemesis.</font>

41:55.040 --> 41:57.840
Yes. Two Valdemars for the price
of one.

41:57.880 --> 41:59.320
I shall complain to my agent.

41:59.360 --> 42:01.080
(LAUGHTER)

42:02.480 --> 42:05.440
<font color="#00ffff">DE VERE: Lately you've been involved</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in a hugely successful run</font>

42:05.480 --> 42:07.200
<font color="#00ffff">at International British Pictures.</font>

42:07.240 --> 42:10.680
<font color="#00ffff">Your Montressor in The Cask</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Amontillado being</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a particular pleasure.</font>

42:10.720 --> 42:13.240
VALDEMAR: You are very kind.
<font color="#00ffff">It would be fair to say</font>

42:13.280 --> 42:15.760
<font color="#00ffff">that it is the part of Akhenaten</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that made your name.</font>

42:15.800 --> 42:17.600
Yes, you could say that, yes.

42:17.640 --> 42:20.240
<font color="#00ffff">The production, unusually, was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">filmed in Egypt.</font>

42:20.280 --> 42:22.160
It was.

42:22.200 --> 42:26.520
Well, our producer, Meriam,
was such a stickler for authenticity.

42:26.560 --> 42:28.200
(DISCORDANT ORGAN CHORD)
She...

42:28.240 --> 42:29.920
Wha... What?

42:31.400 --> 42:33.360
(WOMAN CRIES OUT)

42:35.520 --> 42:36.840
<font color="#ffff00">(SCREAMS)</font>

42:37.720 --> 42:39.240
<font color="#00ff00">(CRIES OF SHOCK)</font>

43:12.240 --> 43:15.440
<font color="#ffff00">Is this a regular haunt for you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">then, er... Reginald?</font>

43:15.480 --> 43:19.440
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, sometimes. When Mrs Bright</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is out for the evening.</font>

43:19.480 --> 43:22.640
<font color="#ffff00">Where's she off to tonight, then?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Down the bingo?</font>

43:22.680 --> 43:26.600
<font color="#00ff00">No. I believe it's the Unmarried</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mothers.</font>

43:26.640 --> 43:29.520
Mrs Bright does a lot of good works.

43:29.560 --> 43:31.240
<font color="#00ff00">What line of work are you in,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Charles?</font>

43:31.280 --> 43:33.720
<font color="#ffff00">I've a warehouse. Shadwell Basin.</font>

43:33.760 --> 43:35.600
<font color="#ffff00">Thursday & Co.</font>

43:35.640 --> 43:37.200
<font color="#ffff00">Funny how the world turns.</font>

43:37.240 --> 43:40.200
<font color="#ffff00">Our old man used to bare-knuckle it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for a shift at the same gaff</font>

43:40.240 --> 43:42.520
<font color="#ffff00">that's now got my name</font>
<font color="#ffff00">over the door.</font>

43:42.560 --> 43:45.200
Mr Bright doesn't want to hear about
that. Sorry, sir.

43:45.240 --> 43:48.360
<font color="#00ff00">Not at all. It's...fascinating.</font>

43:48.400 --> 43:52.120
<font color="#00ff00">I think we can dispense with</font>
<font color="#00ff00">formalities this evening, Thursday.</font>

43:52.160 --> 43:55.840
Yes, sir. Mr... Er, Reginald. Right,
sir.

43:55.880 --> 43:57.440
Sergeant.
<font color="#00ffff">Strange! Good heavens.</font>

43:57.480 --> 44:01.320
<font color="#00ffff">Sorry to interrupt your evening,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">sir, but there's been an incident</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at the Roxy.</font>

44:03.400 --> 44:06.720
<font color="#00ff00">What on earth is going on? </font><font color="#ffffff">It's the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">organist, sir. Leslie Garnier.</font>

44:06.760 --> 44:10.240
I have the audience out of the
auditorium and into the bars
and corridors.

44:10.280 --> 44:13.560
<font color="#ffff00">What about the staff? </font><font color="#ffffff">Guarding the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">exits. Eddie Nero's here.</font>

44:13.600 --> 44:16.680
He's in the manager's flat
with the rest of the VIPs.

44:16.720 --> 44:18.200
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

44:18.240 --> 44:20.600
<font color="#ffff00">Uniform taking down particulars?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, sir.</font>

44:21.600 --> 44:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">Do you have any idea how long we'll</font>
<font color="#ffff00">be here? We're on set at</font>
<font color="#ffff00">seven o'clock</font>

44:26.400 --> 44:28.120
<font color="#ffff00">and Emil's in make-up at five.</font>

44:28.160 --> 44:29.560
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid not, Mr Xarkoff.</font>

44:29.600 --> 44:32.200
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps, in the meantime,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I could freshen your glasses?</font>

44:32.240 --> 44:35.280
<font color="#00ffff">Well, I was hoping to present this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">after the interview</font>

44:35.320 --> 44:37.760
<font color="#00ffff">on behalf of Jephson Cinemas,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Valdemar.</font>

44:37.800 --> 44:40.640
<font color="#00ffff">A small token of our appreciation</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and admiration.</font>

44:40.680 --> 44:43.960
Oh, how very kind.

44:55.720 --> 44:57.800
What is the meaning of this?

44:57.840 --> 44:59.080
(SLAMS BOX DOWN)

44:59.120 --> 45:01.360
<font color="#00ffff">Kenneth, what happened to the watch?</font>

45:01.400 --> 45:05.000
<font color="#00ff00">I've no idea, sir. I put it in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">there myself. </font><font color="#00ffff">I'm so sorry,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Valdemar.</font>

45:05.040 --> 45:07.240
<font color="#00ffff">There's clearly been a mix-up.</font>

45:07.280 --> 45:09.760
<font color="#00ffff">Take it away, Kenneth, take it away.</font>

45:13.840 --> 45:16.480
<font color="#00ff00">Could it have been natural causes?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Well, it could.</font>

45:16.520 --> 45:19.000
But we've one death
connected to the cinema already.

45:19.040 --> 45:20.840
I thought it best not to take
chances.

45:20.880 --> 45:22.880
<font color="#00ff00">But no reason to suspect anything</font>
<font color="#00ff00">untoward?</font>

45:22.920 --> 45:26.200
Garnier said he saw Beavis talking
to somebody on the fire escape.

45:26.240 --> 45:28.640
Maybe that same someone saw Garnier
talking to us.

45:28.680 --> 45:30.600
<font color="#ffff00">Or maybe Garnier went to them.</font>

45:30.640 --> 45:32.080
<font color="#00ff00">Blackmail?</font>

45:32.120 --> 45:34.480
I saw him take a drink from the bar
at eight o'clock.

45:34.520 --> 45:38.600
<font color="#00ff00">And he collapsed at half-past nine.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">If it was Strychnine in the Martini,</font>

45:38.640 --> 45:40.400
<font color="#00ff00">he'd have felt the effects</font>
<font color="#00ff00">much later.</font>

45:40.440 --> 45:43.840
<font color="#ffff00">What if it was something faster</font>
<font color="#ffff00">acting? </font><font color="#00ff00">Or he was poisoned earlier.</font>

45:43.880 --> 45:48.840
<font color="#00ff00">Either are possible, of course. But</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid I won't be able to give</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you a definitive answer</font>

45:48.880 --> 45:51.080
<font color="#00ff00">until I've got the results of his</font>
<font color="#00ff00">blood.</font>

45:52.480 --> 45:56.080
<font color="#00ffff">But you can't imagine any of the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">guests had anything to do with</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Leslie's death?</font>

45:56.120 --> 45:59.120
<font color="#00ffff">They never met him till today.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It's unlikely, sir, I grant you,</font>

45:59.160 --> 46:02.760
<font color="#ffff00">but they may have seen or heard</font>
<font color="#ffff00">something that has a bearing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on our inquiries.</font>

46:02.800 --> 46:05.520
<font color="#00ffff">He's had some sort of heart attack,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">hasn't he? Or a seizure.</font>

46:05.560 --> 46:09.560
We won't know the cause of Mr
Garnier's death until after
the post-mortem is concluded.

46:09.600 --> 46:13.520
But it is the second sudden death
connected to the Roxy in the last
three days.

46:13.560 --> 46:15.320
<font color="#ffff00">What's your business with Eddie</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Nero?</font>

46:15.360 --> 46:17.640
<font color="#ffff00">You were seen in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">private conversation with him.</font>

46:17.680 --> 46:20.840
<font color="#00ffff">He's a guest of Mr Jephson Junior,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the son of the owner.</font>

46:20.880 --> 46:24.200
<font color="#00ffff">He generously offered to take</font>
<font color="#00ffff">everyone out to dinner at his club.</font>

46:27.720 --> 46:30.440
<font color="#00ffff">Ladies and gentlemen,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">if I might have your attention,</font>

46:30.480 --> 46:32.640
<font color="#00ffff">these gentlemen are from the police.</font>

46:32.680 --> 46:36.800
<font color="#ffff00">Detective Chief Inspector Thursday,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Detective Sergeant Morse,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Thames Valley.</font>

46:36.840 --> 46:39.440
<font color="#ffff00">We'll try not to detain you any</font>
<font color="#ffff00">longer than necessary,</font>

46:39.480 --> 46:42.720
<font color="#ffff00">but we will need to ask questions</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of all of you in turn.</font>

46:44.000 --> 46:47.000
<font color="#ffff00">All right, Carol,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I think you'd better cut along home.</font>

46:47.040 --> 46:50.000
<font color="#ffff00">Morse'll get a constable to drive</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you back. Morse?</font>

46:51.760 --> 46:54.920
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Jephson,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if I could start with you.</font>

46:54.960 --> 46:56.720
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know what was in that box,</font>

46:56.760 --> 46:59.760
<font color="#ffff00">but that poor old man looked like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he'd had an awful shock.</font>

47:01.200 --> 47:03.040
Here, let me.

47:08.120 --> 47:11.800
<font color="#ffff00">Well, thanks for a...memorable</font>
<font color="#ffff00">evening.</font>

47:13.440 --> 47:17.080
<font color="#ffff00">I don't suppose I'll be seeing you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">again before we go back.</font>

47:17.120 --> 47:22.120
Well, I...don't see how I can
compete with Jason Curwen.

47:23.520 --> 47:24.880
<font color="#ffff00">It wasn't a mistake.</font>

47:26.880 --> 47:29.160
<font color="#ffff00">Not everything has to be more than</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it is.</font>

47:30.120 --> 47:32.440
Constable Davis will see you home.
Davis.

47:32.480 --> 47:35.520
This is DCI Thursday's niece.
If you could... <font color="#ffff00">Hiya.</font>

47:40.600 --> 47:43.200
<font color="#ffff00">Doesn't matter what stone I turn</font>
<font color="#ffff00">over, does it?</font>

47:43.240 --> 47:45.240
<font color="#00ffff">I'm a great patron of the arts.</font>

47:45.280 --> 47:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">Ask anyone that knows me.</font>

47:47.600 --> 47:50.360
<font color="#ffff00">You wouldn't get out of bed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">unless there was a dollar in it.</font>

47:50.400 --> 47:53.120
<font color="#ffff00">What's your business with De Vere?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Nothing.</font>

47:53.160 --> 47:55.000
<font color="#00ffff">I met him through the owner.</font>

47:55.040 --> 47:57.480
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Jephson and I are in business</font>
<font color="#00ffff">together.</font>

47:57.520 --> 48:01.720
Have you ever had any dealings
with Leslie Garnier? The organist.

48:01.760 --> 48:04.760
<font color="#00ffff">I'm more of an Errol Garner man</font>
<font color="#00ffff">myself.</font>

48:04.800 --> 48:06.720
What about Ronald Beavis?

48:06.760 --> 48:10.720
<font color="#00ffff">The only Ronald Beavis I know is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ronnie Beavis. One of yours,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">out of Banbury.</font>

48:10.760 --> 48:14.200
<font color="#00ffff">Tried to fit me up on a B&E charge</font>
<font color="#00ffff">once.</font>

48:14.240 --> 48:16.400
<font color="#00ffff">I haven't seen him in donkeys. Why?</font>

48:19.240 --> 48:21.600
<font color="#00ffff">So is that it, then? I can go?</font>

48:21.640 --> 48:23.000
<font color="#ffff00">For the minute.</font>

48:25.040 --> 48:27.040
<font color="#ffff00">You never asked about the arson.</font>

48:27.960 --> 48:30.200
<font color="#ffff00">Khartoum Street, now this Public</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Advice Centre.</font>

48:30.240 --> 48:32.080
<font color="#ffff00">That makes two of yours in as many</font>
<font color="#ffff00">days.</font>

48:32.120 --> 48:34.800
<font color="#00ffff">Be these racialists, I'd have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">thought, wouldn't you?</font>

48:34.840 --> 48:37.480
<font color="#ffff00">Nice little earner.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Shovelling them up from the airport,</font>

48:37.520 --> 48:39.320
<font color="#ffff00">bussing them off to Christ knows</font>
<font color="#ffff00">where.</font>

48:39.360 --> 48:41.800
<font color="#ffff00">How many more dossers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you got like that around town?</font>

48:41.840 --> 48:45.520
<font color="#00ffff">If they weren't renting off me,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it'd all be on the council,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wouldn't it?</font>

48:45.560 --> 48:49.160
<font color="#00ffff">Should be some sort of civic award</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for people like me.</font>

48:49.840 --> 48:52.680
<font color="#ffff00">Don't hold your breath. Second</font>
<font color="#ffff00">thoughts...</font>

48:52.720 --> 48:55.440
<font color="#ffff00">Go on, you're done for now.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">(SCOFFS)</font>

48:55.480 --> 48:58.240
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: So you hadn't met Mr</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Garnier? </font><font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

48:58.280 --> 49:01.040
There really isn't much
I can tell you.

49:01.080 --> 49:05.240
I was up here until the manager came
to collect me a few minutes
before I was due on.

49:05.280 --> 49:08.520
<font color="#ffff00">Did anyone bring you a Martini</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the bar? </font><font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

49:08.560 --> 49:13.440
The manager, Mr De Vere, did offer to
bring me a little tincture.

49:13.480 --> 49:15.840
But it must have slipped his mind.

49:15.880 --> 49:18.600
I understand
you had something of a shock earlier.

49:19.600 --> 49:21.640
A gift from the management.

49:21.680 --> 49:24.080
They wanted to give me a watch.

49:25.440 --> 49:27.440
Which had gone astray.

49:29.200 --> 49:33.720
But on top of this awful thing
with that man dying,

49:33.760 --> 49:36.640
I really didn't think it was the
right time or place.

49:38.040 --> 49:41.320
<font color="#ffff00">You knew him well, the organist?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Leslie? Oh, yes, sir.</font>

49:41.360 --> 49:43.480
<font color="#00ff00">Best part of ten years, I should</font>
<font color="#00ff00">think.</font>

49:43.520 --> 49:48.360
<font color="#00ff00">I came across from the Stoll-Moss</font>
<font color="#00ff00">circuit and Leslie was already</font>
<font color="#00ff00">installed.</font>

49:48.400 --> 49:50.280
<font color="#00ff00">Very nice gentleman.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Variety?</font>

49:50.320 --> 49:51.640
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, yes, sir.</font>

49:51.680 --> 49:54.080
<font color="#00ff00">I've opened the doors for all the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">greats.</font>

49:54.120 --> 49:56.480
<font color="#00ff00">It's probably why Leslie and I got</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on so well.</font>

49:56.520 --> 49:59.360
<font color="#ffff00">We'll need a next of kin.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">He was a single man, sir.</font>

49:59.400 --> 50:01.000
<font color="#00ff00">Much like myself.</font>

50:01.040 --> 50:02.840
<font color="#00ff00">I'll miss my pal.</font>

50:02.880 --> 50:04.800
<font color="#00ff00">He always had a friendly word.</font>

50:04.840 --> 50:07.680
<font color="#00ff00">And he was a master</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of the Compton. </font><font color="#ffffff">The organ, sir.</font>

50:07.720 --> 50:10.560
<font color="#00ff00">I used to play a bit myself, sir.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">The piano.</font>

50:10.600 --> 50:13.240
<font color="#00ff00">In my younger days, of course,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">before um...</font>

50:13.280 --> 50:15.040
<font color="#00ff00">Well, king and country, sir.</font>

50:15.080 --> 50:17.840
<font color="#00ff00">So we had that in common, too:</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the music.</font>

50:17.880 --> 50:20.680
What happened to the man
who caused the disturbance earlier?

50:20.720 --> 50:23.640
<font color="#00ff00">I threw him out on his ear, sir,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on the street, where he belongs.</font>

50:23.680 --> 50:26.840
<font color="#00ff00">I know Arabs, sir. You can't trust</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a-one of them.</font>

50:28.000 --> 50:29.960
<font color="#ffff00">All right, you go about your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">business.</font>

50:30.000 --> 50:31.880
<font color="#ffff00">A constable will take</font>
<font color="#ffff00">over from here.</font>

50:31.920 --> 50:35.000
<font color="#ffff00">He was popular with the rest of the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">staff, Miss Persky?</font>

50:35.040 --> 50:38.280
<font color="#00ff00">I think he'd had a falling out with</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mr De Vere.</font>

50:38.320 --> 50:42.400
<font color="#00ff00">I couldn't say what over,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but I just heard Mr De Vere say,</font>

50:42.440 --> 50:44.800
<font color="#00ff00">"Don't you threaten me," or</font>
<font color="#00ff00">something like that.</font>

50:44.840 --> 50:48.520
When was this? <font color="#00ff00">Last night, during the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">first feature.</font>

50:50.320 --> 50:52.480
Did you make Mr Garnier a Martini?

50:52.520 --> 50:57.200
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, no, sir. Usually he'd have one</font>
<font color="#00ff00">waiting for him on the organ</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to sip at.</font>

50:57.240 --> 51:01.000
<font color="#00ff00">Part of his act. You know, he'd</font>
<font color="#00ff00">raise his glass to the audience.</font>

51:01.040 --> 51:06.560
<font color="#00ff00">But we were under strict orders from</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mr De Vere to keep him straight.</font>

51:08.160 --> 51:10.720
<font color="#ffff00">He threatened you? With what?</font>

51:10.760 --> 51:12.680
<font color="#00ffff">Said he wanted to quit.</font>

51:12.720 --> 51:14.640
<font color="#00ffff">Not for the first time.</font>

51:14.680 --> 51:16.680
<font color="#00ffff">I called his bluff.</font>

51:17.760 --> 51:21.040
<font color="#00ffff">Leslie had a weakness for the booze.</font>

51:21.080 --> 51:24.840
<font color="#00ffff">The whole National Anthem thing was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so he could get out of here and get</font>
<font color="#00ffff">into the pub.</font>

51:24.880 --> 51:27.360
<font color="#ffff00">You liked him?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

51:28.200 --> 51:30.200
<font color="#00ffff">Apart from the drink.</font>

51:30.240 --> 51:32.760
<font color="#00ffff">I felt a bit sorry for him,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">truth be told.</font>

51:32.800 --> 51:36.040
<font color="#00ffff">He played all over the world, you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">know. On the liners, after the war.</font>

51:36.080 --> 51:40.280
<font color="#00ffff">I expect coming to the Roxy was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a bit of a comedown,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">after that sort of life.</font>

51:41.480 --> 51:44.160
You put a drink on the bar earlier
in the lounge.

51:44.200 --> 51:46.240
Who was that for?
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Valdemar.</font>

51:46.280 --> 51:49.080
<font color="#00ffff">Mr De Vere asked me to.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">But Mr Garnier took it.</font>

51:49.120 --> 51:52.440
<font color="#00ffff">I wouldn't know, sir. I set it on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the bar, turned round to take</font>
<font color="#00ffff">another order</font>

51:52.480 --> 51:56.600
<font color="#00ffff">and when I looked back, it had gone.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I thought Mr De Vere must have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">collected it.</font>

51:56.640 --> 52:00.680
I believe there was something
of an upset earlier with Mr Valdemar.

52:00.720 --> 52:02.800
Something to do with a present?
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, yeah.</font>

52:02.840 --> 52:05.600
<font color="#00ffff">Mr De Vere bought him a watch</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as a thank you from the cinema.</font>

52:05.640 --> 52:08.080
<font color="#00ffff">He showed it to us when he fetched</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it back.</font>

52:08.120 --> 52:10.280
<font color="#00ffff">He asked me to find a nice box</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for it.</font>

52:10.320 --> 52:14.400
<font color="#00ffff">I got hold of one, put the watch</font>
<font color="#00ffff">inside and left it in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr De Vere's office.</font>

52:14.440 --> 52:18.600
So anyone could have had access to
it? <font color="#00ffff">Sure.</font>

52:18.640 --> 52:21.880
What was in the box when he opened
it? <font color="#00ffff">Funny-looking little thing.</font>

52:23.160 --> 52:25.040
<font color="#00ffff">See for yourself.</font>

52:40.000 --> 52:42.000
(BIRDSONG)

52:44.920 --> 52:48.240
MORSE: I'll need a list of everyone
in the audience as soon as you can.

52:49.360 --> 52:52.160
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah. We'll cadge a lift back off</font>
<font color="#00ffff">uniform, eh?</font>

52:52.200 --> 52:54.960
You go on.
<font color="#00ffff">All right, fine. Been a long night.</font>

52:55.000 --> 52:57.720
I don't suppose Valdemar's still
here, is he? <font color="#ffff00">Gone. Why?</font>

52:57.760 --> 52:59.760
That present that he was given.

53:00.520 --> 53:02.560
<font color="#ffff00">Hieroglyphics?</font>

53:02.600 --> 53:05.200
<font color="#ffff00">Is someone playing a joke on him?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Don't know.</font>

53:05.240 --> 53:08.160
But if that glass Garnier took from
the bar does contain poison,

53:08.200 --> 53:09.840
he wasn't the intended victim.

53:09.880 --> 53:12.360
The drink was meant for Valdemar.

53:14.640 --> 53:16.720
(DOOR OPENS)

53:16.760 --> 53:19.920
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Thanks.</font>

53:19.960 --> 53:22.320
(DOOR CREAKS)

53:25.560 --> 53:27.960
(COOING)

53:41.680 --> 53:42.800
(THUD)

53:46.400 --> 53:48.280
(BELL CHIMES IN DISTANCE)

53:53.520 --> 53:54.720
(KEYS CLINK)

54:01.800 --> 54:03.280
Pissed the bed?

54:03.320 --> 54:05.000
<font color="#ffff00">You know me, Fred.</font>

54:05.040 --> 54:06.960
<font color="#ffff00">Early riser. Always have been.</font>

54:07.000 --> 54:09.800
<font color="#ffff00">Cup of tea? One just brewed.</font>

54:10.840 --> 54:12.760
<font color="#ffff00">It's the business.</font>

54:12.800 --> 54:14.440
<font color="#ffff00">I need a loan.</font>

54:14.480 --> 54:18.240
<font color="#ffff00">Only short-term, just so I can make</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the payroll this month.</font>

54:18.280 --> 54:22.600
<font color="#ffff00">You'll get it back. Every last</font>
<font color="#ffff00">penny, with interest. I swear.</font>

54:22.640 --> 54:24.520
Can't you go to the bank?

54:24.560 --> 54:26.560
<font color="#ffff00">I'm in it with them up to here.</font>

54:27.680 --> 54:30.280
And that's all it is? No-one's
leaning on you? The twins?

54:30.320 --> 54:32.320
<font color="#ffff00">No, no, nothing like that.</font>

54:35.160 --> 54:36.960
Well...

54:37.840 --> 54:39.920
..I've only ever had a copper's
wages.

54:39.960 --> 54:42.120
Two kids, mortgage.

54:44.040 --> 54:46.040
I've got the pension to fall back
on.

54:46.080 --> 54:47.560
We've got a bit put by.

54:48.720 --> 54:50.120
But I'm no Rockefeller.

54:50.160 --> 54:52.320
And I'd need to talk to Win.

54:54.440 --> 54:56.360
How much are we talking about?

54:57.760 --> 54:58.880
<font color="#ffff00">(SIGHS)</font>

54:58.920 --> 55:01.440
(BELL CHIMES)

55:01.480 --> 55:05.680
<font color="#00ff00">This was stolen from us.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It's a funerary scarab.</font>

55:05.720 --> 55:07.640
<font color="#00ff00">New Kingdom. Armana Period.</font>

55:07.680 --> 55:12.000
<font color="#00ff00">Inscribed with the nomen cartouche</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for the Pharaoh Akhenaten.</font>

55:12.040 --> 55:14.000
<font color="#00ff00">Formerly Amenhotep IV.</font>

55:14.040 --> 55:15.600
<font color="#ffff00">Akhenaten?</font>

55:15.640 --> 55:19.360
<font color="#ffff00">That's the same character</font>
<font color="#ffff00">played by Emil Valdemar, isn't it?</font>

55:19.400 --> 55:22.280
<font color="#00ff00">He wasn't a character.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">He was a ruler of Egypt.</font>

55:22.320 --> 55:23.680
<font color="#00ff00">Come with me, please.</font>

55:27.360 --> 55:29.360
<font color="#00ff00">It went missing from here.</font>

55:34.120 --> 55:36.520
And would Beavis have had keys
to this cabinet?

55:36.560 --> 55:38.920
<font color="#00ff00">He'd certainly know where</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to find a set.</font>

55:38.960 --> 55:42.480
Does it have some sort of special
meaning, this scarab?

55:42.520 --> 55:46.520
<font color="#00ff00">Traditionally, it is placed inside</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the body, in place of the heart.</font>

55:46.560 --> 55:50.840
<font color="#00ff00">It bears also lines from the Book of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Dead.</font>

55:50.880 --> 55:53.640
<font color="#00ff00">An appeal to the heart</font>
<font color="#00ff00">not to speak against the dead.</font>

55:53.680 --> 55:57.000
<font color="#00ff00">If the heart is found wanting</font>
<font color="#00ff00">by the rulers of the afterworld,</font>

55:57.040 --> 56:00.480
<font color="#00ff00">the deceased are barred</font>
<font color="#00ff00">from passing on to the afterlife.</font>

56:01.480 --> 56:04.600
<font color="#00ff00">Where did you come by it? </font><font color="#ffffff">It was at</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the Roxy cinema last night.</font>

56:04.640 --> 56:08.040
<font color="#ffff00">I understand you caused quite a stir</font>
<font color="#ffff00">there, Doctor.</font>

56:08.080 --> 56:10.000
<font color="#00ff00">So would you, Chief Inspector.</font>

56:10.040 --> 56:13.120
<font color="#00ff00">These films are a travesty.</font>

56:13.160 --> 56:15.360
<font color="#00ff00">A calumny upon Egypt and all</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Egyptians.</font>

56:15.400 --> 56:17.240
<font color="#ffff00">(SCOFFS) Just a bit of fun, surely?</font>

56:17.280 --> 56:18.880
<font color="#00ff00">There is a time for fun.</font>

56:18.920 --> 56:21.080
<font color="#00ff00">My country's at war with Israel.</font>

56:21.120 --> 56:23.320
<font color="#00ff00">A situation you British created.</font>

56:24.440 --> 56:28.000
<font color="#00ff00">My own son was shot down over Suez</font>
<font color="#00ff00">last July.</font>

56:29.000 --> 56:31.040
<font color="#00ff00">These films, this nonsense,</font>

56:31.080 --> 56:34.680
<font color="#00ff00">makes a mockery of the history</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and culture he died to defend.</font>

56:36.080 --> 56:38.080
<font color="#ffff00">Forgive me, Dr Shoukry.</font>

56:40.640 --> 56:44.080
<font color="#ffff00">One father to another,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you have my condolences.</font>

56:48.160 --> 56:50.600
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: Are you absolutely sure,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Dr DeBryn?</font>

56:51.400 --> 56:54.600
<font color="#00ff00">Cyanide.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Not strychnine?</font>

56:54.640 --> 56:59.960
<font color="#00ff00">I found the remains of a capsule of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the same stuffed inside the olive</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in the Martini.</font>

57:00.000 --> 57:04.600
<font color="#00ff00">As the alcohol dissolved the casing,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">so the cyanide seeped out.</font>

57:05.840 --> 57:07.640
<font color="#ffff00">It was meant for Valdemar, then.</font>

57:07.680 --> 57:10.600
Valdemar said he'd never met
Garnier. <font color="#ffff00">Yeah. Why?</font>

57:10.640 --> 57:12.080
Autograph book.

57:12.120 --> 57:16.040
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, yes. That was in his jacket,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">along with his wallet.</font>

57:16.080 --> 57:19.560
MORSE: Final entry.
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: "Emil Valdemar."</font>

57:22.360 --> 57:25.560
<font color="#00ff00">Mr Garnier certainly had</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a collection of the great</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and the good.</font>

57:25.600 --> 57:27.360
<font color="#00ff00">Looks like a lifetime's hobby.</font>

57:27.400 --> 57:31.040
<font color="#00ff00">Gracie Fields, George Formby,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Laurel and Hardy.</font>

57:31.080 --> 57:34.280
<font color="#ffff00">Must have been their last tour, sir,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">1953. I tried to get tickets.</font>

57:34.320 --> 57:37.280
<font color="#00ff00">Worth a lot of money, I should</font>
<font color="#00ff00">think to a collector.</font>

57:37.320 --> 57:40.920
But the point is, Garnier must have
seen Valdemar in order to get his
signature.

57:40.960 --> 57:43.960
<font color="#00ff00">Why did Valdemar deny it?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Seems a trivial matter to lie about.</font>

57:44.000 --> 57:48.480
<font color="#00ffff">So, Beavis nicks this beetle, or</font>
<font color="#00ffff">whatever it is, from the Pitt-Rivers</font>

57:48.520 --> 57:50.680
<font color="#00ffff">and tries to flog it to...who?</font>

57:51.560 --> 57:53.680
<font color="#00ffff">And how did it get to be in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Valdemar's gift?</font>

57:53.720 --> 57:56.320
The only prints in it are mine,
Valdemar's and Beavis's.

57:56.360 --> 57:58.920
<font color="#00ff00">Valdemar had no connection to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Beavis, so far as we know?</font>

57:58.960 --> 58:01.360
<font color="#ffff00">Not that we've been able to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">establish yet, sir.</font>

58:01.400 --> 58:03.520
<font color="#ffff00">Strange is also looking at all the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">staff</font>

58:03.560 --> 58:05.520
<font color="#ffff00">to see if their paths crossed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Beavis.</font>

58:05.560 --> 58:07.640
<font color="#00ff00">From his time at County, you mean?</font>

58:07.680 --> 58:11.360
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, sir. There may be more among</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Garnier's belongings might shed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">light.</font>

58:11.400 --> 58:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">Constable Fancy's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">collecting evidence from his flat</font>

58:14.200 --> 58:16.480
<font color="#ffff00">while Morse and me brace Valdemar.</font>

58:16.520 --> 58:18.840
<font color="#00ff00">You think he might have been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the intended victim?</font>

58:18.880 --> 58:22.600
If the glass that Garnier took from
the bar was poisoned, almost
certainly.

58:52.280 --> 58:54.280
<font color="#00ffff">ASSISTANT DIRECTOR: Ready?</font>

58:54.320 --> 58:55.720
<font color="#00ffff">Stand by!</font>

58:55.760 --> 58:57.840
<font color="#00ffff">Roll sound!</font>

58:57.880 --> 58:59.640
<font color="#00ffff">Roll camera!</font>

59:00.640 --> 59:01.920
<font color="#00ffff">Action!</font>

59:12.400 --> 59:14.400
<font color="#ffff00">EMIL: Victoria!</font>

59:15.280 --> 59:16.680
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria!</font>

59:16.720 --> 59:18.560
Over here, Professor!

59:18.600 --> 59:21.800
<font color="#00ffff">And cut! Print! Moving on!</font>

59:27.080 --> 59:29.920
<font color="#00ffff">It is my signature.</font>

59:29.960 --> 59:32.280
But you don't remember signing it
for Mr Garnier?

59:32.320 --> 59:35.240
<font color="#00ffff">When you've been signing autographs</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for as long as I have,</font>

59:35.280 --> 59:37.840
<font color="#00ffff">I could have signed dozens yesterday</font>
<font color="#00ffff">evening.</font>

59:37.880 --> 59:40.160
<font color="#00ffff">You don't notice people's faces.</font>

59:40.200 --> 59:42.640
<font color="#00ffff">But Akhenaten's cartouche:</font>

59:42.680 --> 59:45.400
<font color="#00ffff">I would not commit that mark</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to paper.</font>

59:46.040 --> 59:47.760
<font color="#ffff00">Why not, sir?</font>

59:47.800 --> 59:50.840
<font color="#00ffff">The Pharaoh's Curse was well named.</font>

59:52.360 --> 59:55.120
<font color="#00ffff">Of all the people involved in that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">production...</font>

59:56.800 --> 59:59.680
<font color="#00ffff">..I am the last one left alive.</font>

01:00:00.440 --> 01:00:02.360
<font color="#ffff00">Is that so unusual, sir?</font>

01:00:02.400 --> 01:00:05.800
<font color="#ffff00">You were a relatively young man</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when the picture was made</font>

01:00:05.840 --> 01:00:07.880
<font color="#ffff00">and, well...</font>

01:00:07.920 --> 01:00:09.840
<font color="#00ffff">Now I'm an old man.</font>

01:00:09.880 --> 01:00:11.880
<font color="#00ffff">Maybe so.</font>

01:00:13.040 --> 01:00:15.560
<font color="#00ffff">But within a year,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">two of the cast members were dead.</font>

01:00:15.600 --> 01:00:18.080
<font color="#00ffff">The director died in a plane crash.</font>

01:00:18.120 --> 01:00:21.680
<font color="#00ffff">It's been like that ever since.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Every year, one or two more.</font>

01:00:21.720 --> 01:00:23.760
That's Hollywood hyperbole, surely?

01:00:23.800 --> 01:00:26.200
Something to help sell the film.

01:00:26.240 --> 01:00:28.560
<font color="#00ffff">Would that it were.</font>

01:00:28.600 --> 01:00:30.760
<font color="#ffff00">What made you think there was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">something to it?</font>

01:00:30.800 --> 01:00:33.680
<font color="#00ffff">We shot exteriors on location,</font>

01:00:33.720 --> 01:00:35.640
<font color="#00ffff">but when we returned to the studio</font>

01:00:35.680 --> 01:00:39.120
<font color="#00ffff">we were using properties</font>
<font color="#00ffff">loaned to us by Hearst.</font>

01:00:39.160 --> 01:00:43.840
<font color="#00ffff">Genuine antiquities he'd acquired</font>
<font color="#00ffff">some way or another.</font>

01:00:43.880 --> 01:00:48.840
<font color="#00ffff">A delegation from the Egyptian</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Consulate tried</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to picket the studio.</font>

01:00:50.480 --> 01:00:54.040
<font color="#00ffff">They said we were desecrating their</font>
<font color="#00ffff">rites and sacred relics...</font>

01:00:56.080 --> 01:00:58.640
<font color="#00ffff">..and no good would come of it.</font>

01:00:58.680 --> 01:01:04.120
And what happened? <font color="#00ffff">Oh, the studio had</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the police move them on.</font>

01:01:04.160 --> 01:01:06.880
<font color="#00ffff">They're a superstitious, vengeful</font>
<font color="#00ffff">people.</font>

01:01:08.120 --> 01:01:10.520
<font color="#00ffff">I know. I saw enough of them</font>
<font color="#00ffff">during the Great War.</font>

01:01:10.560 --> 01:01:13.560
<font color="#ffff00">I was up the desert too, sir, in the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">second go.</font>

01:01:14.640 --> 01:01:16.200
<font color="#00ffff">Then you know what I mean.</font>

01:01:16.240 --> 01:01:19.400
So that's why you reacted as you did
when you saw the scarab?

01:01:21.480 --> 01:01:23.680
<font color="#00ffff">I used to think it was a load of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">nonsense.</font>

01:01:25.840 --> 01:01:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">Now I'm not so sure.</font>

01:01:28.760 --> 01:01:30.680
<font color="#00ffff">Emile. We're ready for you.</font>

01:01:32.200 --> 01:01:34.920
<font color="#00ffff">I'm afraid there's really nothing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">more I can tell you.</font>

01:01:36.040 --> 01:01:38.040
<font color="#00ffff">I might have signed that autograph,</font>

01:01:38.080 --> 01:01:43.480
<font color="#00ffff">but I would never...never use</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the cartouche of Akhenaten.</font>

01:02:02.120 --> 01:02:04.120
<font color="#ffff00">It's a rum go, and no mistake.</font>

01:02:06.200 --> 01:02:08.400
<font color="#ffff00">What do you make of Dr Shoukry?</font>

01:02:09.520 --> 01:02:11.640
Well, he has a fair grievance,
I suppose.

01:02:11.680 --> 01:02:14.280
Bad enough to see
its nation's treasures plundered,

01:02:14.320 --> 01:02:17.320
but to watch its culture turned into
cheap thrills...

01:02:17.360 --> 01:02:19.120
<font color="#ffff00">Enough to kill someone over, though?</font>

01:02:19.160 --> 01:02:22.640
<font color="#00ffff">The cinema's Assistant Manager,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Kenneth Bullings, sir.</font>

01:02:22.680 --> 01:02:24.480
<font color="#00ffff">13th of January, 1941.</font>

01:02:24.520 --> 01:02:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">He has form for theft, affray: most</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of it juvenile.</font>

01:02:27.880 --> 01:02:31.400
<font color="#00ffff">But we've an ABH in 1958 handled by</font>
<font color="#00ffff">County.</font>

01:02:31.440 --> 01:02:34.280
<font color="#00ffff">The investigating officer was Ronald</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Beavis.</font>

01:02:44.840 --> 01:02:48.560
<font color="#ffff00">You've got something of a chequered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">past, Mr Bullings.</font>

01:02:50.040 --> 01:02:55.840
<font color="#ffff00">Affray, assault, occasioning actual</font>
<font color="#ffff00">bodily harm.</font>

01:02:55.880 --> 01:02:58.120
<font color="#ffff00">Do you remember who pinched you on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that?</font>

01:02:58.160 --> 01:03:00.080
<font color="#00ffff">That was ten years ago.</font>

01:03:00.120 --> 01:03:01.400
<font color="#00ffff">No, I don't.</font>

01:03:01.440 --> 01:03:05.960
<font color="#ffff00">Then you'd be surprised to learn it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was Ronald Beavis, a patron</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the Roxy.</font>

01:03:06.000 --> 01:03:08.040
<font color="#ffff00">He was at The Pharaoh's Curse the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">other night</font>

01:03:08.080 --> 01:03:10.400
<font color="#ffff00">and found dead in his flat the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">following morning.</font>

01:03:10.440 --> 01:03:13.640
<font color="#ffff00">Poisoned. Just like Mr Garnier.</font>

01:03:14.840 --> 01:03:16.760
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know anything about that.</font>

01:03:17.840 --> 01:03:19.840
<font color="#ffff00">Is that the truth, Kenneth?</font>

01:03:21.040 --> 01:03:23.120
<font color="#ffff00">Cos if you are involved in some way,</font>

01:03:23.160 --> 01:03:26.840
<font color="#ffff00">you'd feel so much better if you got</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it off your chest, I promise you.</font>

01:03:27.760 --> 01:03:30.680
You didn't mean to kill Garnier,
did you?

01:03:30.720 --> 01:03:33.480
<font color="#00ffff">Listen, I've come here to talk to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you of my own free will.</font>

01:03:33.520 --> 01:03:37.720
<font color="#ffff00">And now you're being interviewed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">under caution, so take thought.</font>

01:03:38.720 --> 01:03:41.960
You made that Martini for
Valdemar. <font color="#00ffff">I told you I did.</font>

01:03:42.000 --> 01:03:45.760
<font color="#00ffff">Just the way he likes it.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">One part Martini to two part vodka.</font>

01:03:45.800 --> 01:03:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">Dash of bitters.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">And an olive.</font>

01:03:47.600 --> 01:03:49.840
<font color="#00ffff">No! Twist. Of lemon.</font>

01:03:51.400 --> 01:03:53.320
Are you sure about that?
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah.</font>

01:03:53.360 --> 01:03:55.360
<font color="#00ffff">He can't bear olives. Famous for it.</font>

01:03:55.400 --> 01:03:57.240
<font color="#00ffff">It was in an interview I read</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with him.</font>

01:03:57.280 --> 01:03:59.360
<font color="#00ffff">They remind him of Egypt.</font>

01:03:59.400 --> 01:04:03.040
<font color="#00ffff">Guess he had too many of them when</font>
<font color="#00ffff">he was making The Pharaoh's Curse.</font>

01:04:08.320 --> 01:04:10.560
<font color="#00ffff">Christ, you think I put something in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his drink.</font>

01:04:12.040 --> 01:04:13.520
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't. Honest.</font>

01:04:13.560 --> 01:04:15.480
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not the same as when I was a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">kid.</font>

01:04:15.520 --> 01:04:17.800
<font color="#00ffff">Ask anyone that knows me.</font>

01:04:17.840 --> 01:04:23.840
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: So, if the Martini Garnier</font>
<font color="#ffff00">took from the bar didn't have an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">olive in it,</font>

01:04:23.880 --> 01:04:26.720
<font color="#ffff00">that means Valdemar's drink wasn't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">poisoned.</font>

01:04:26.760 --> 01:04:28.800
MORSE: And Garnier was the intended
victim.

01:04:28.840 --> 01:04:31.520
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: Nothing to do with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Valdemar and his curse.</font>

01:04:31.560 --> 01:04:33.840
<font color="#ffff00">Which makes the scarab business</font>
<font color="#ffff00">just mischief?</font>

01:04:33.880 --> 01:04:37.400
Pretty extreme mischief, given
the man who stole the scarab
is now dead.

01:04:37.440 --> 01:04:41.360
<font color="#ffff00">We've only got Shoukry's word for it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that Beavis could have taken it,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">don't forget.</font>

01:04:41.400 --> 01:04:44.000
<font color="#ffff00">More to the point, how did Garnier</font>
<font color="#ffff00">come by</font>

01:04:44.040 --> 01:04:46.840
<font color="#ffff00">the poisoned Martini if not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from Bullings?</font>

01:04:46.880 --> 01:04:50.640
<font color="#ffff00">Given his form,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my money's still on Kenneth.</font>

01:04:50.680 --> 01:04:54.960
<font color="#00ff00">When he was younger, yeah,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">he got in with a bad crowd.</font>

01:04:55.000 --> 01:04:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">But he's a good lad at heart.</font>

01:04:56.920 --> 01:05:00.440
<font color="#00ff00">And I should know. I've had the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">raising of him. </font><font color="#ffff00">How's that?</font>

01:05:00.480 --> 01:05:03.000
<font color="#00ff00">His mother upped and went off</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with a Canadian.</font>

01:05:03.040 --> 01:05:06.080
<font color="#00ff00">He didn't want to be landed</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with another bloke's kiddie.</font>

01:05:06.120 --> 01:05:08.000
<font color="#00ff00">So it's just been Ken and me.</font>

01:05:08.040 --> 01:05:09.720
<font color="#00ff00">I've done my best by him.</font>

01:05:09.760 --> 01:05:12.680
Why? Where was his father?
<font color="#00ff00">Tobruk.</font>

01:05:13.880 --> 01:05:15.800
<font color="#00ff00">He was buried out there.</font>

01:05:15.840 --> 01:05:18.360
<font color="#00ff00">Well, what was left of him.</font>

01:05:19.840 --> 01:05:21.240
<font color="#00ff00">Panzer.</font>

01:05:22.880 --> 01:05:24.320
<font color="#00ff00">Flamethrower.</font>

01:05:26.960 --> 01:05:29.240
Oi, what's all this?

01:05:29.280 --> 01:05:31.440
<font color="#00ffff">Everything from Garnier's flat.</font>

01:05:31.480 --> 01:05:32.760
<font color="#00ffff">(GRUNTS)</font>

01:05:34.040 --> 01:05:36.400
<font color="#00ffff">Pays to be thorough. Right?</font>

01:05:36.440 --> 01:05:38.000
<font color="#ffff00">Quite right, Constable.</font>

01:05:38.040 --> 01:05:40.760
<font color="#00ffff">It's mostly old tat from Garnier's</font>
<font color="#00ffff">travels, sir.</font>

01:05:40.800 --> 01:05:42.240
<font color="#00ffff">I brought his post, too.</font>

01:05:42.280 --> 01:05:44.360
<font color="#00ffff">Bills and final demands, as far as I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">can see.</font>

01:05:44.400 --> 01:05:47.280
Put them on the evidence
table and I'll give it a look through

01:05:47.320 --> 01:05:49.960
once I've been through the audience
particulars.

01:06:08.120 --> 01:06:11.160
(DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES)

01:06:13.760 --> 01:06:15.800
Evening, Pop. Guilia.

01:06:16.960 --> 01:06:19.360
So, have you got what I came for?

01:06:22.000 --> 01:06:23.320
(TILL DINGS)

01:06:27.680 --> 01:06:30.120
There. That wasn't so hard, was it?

01:06:31.160 --> 01:06:32.560
Guilia.

01:06:33.280 --> 01:06:35.560
(DOOR OPENS, BELL JANGLES)

01:06:53.800 --> 01:06:55.000
<font color="#ffff00">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:06:59.160 --> 01:07:01.120
(LIAM GROANS)

01:07:04.640 --> 01:07:07.000
<font color="#00ff00">Liam Flynn. Died in the ambulance.</font>

01:07:07.040 --> 01:07:08.680
<font color="#00ff00">Three stab wounds,</font>

01:07:08.720 --> 01:07:11.280
<font color="#00ff00">two of which would have tested the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">finest of surgeons.</font>

01:07:11.320 --> 01:07:13.240
<font color="#00ff00">Blade about six inches long.</font>

01:07:13.280 --> 01:07:15.480
<font color="#00ff00">There's not much more I can tell</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you, I'm afraid.</font>

01:07:15.520 --> 01:07:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">All right, Doctor, thank you very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">much.</font>

01:07:19.560 --> 01:07:20.960
<font color="#ffff00">Flynn.</font>

01:07:21.000 --> 01:07:22.920
<font color="#ffff00">One of Eddie Nero's men, isn't he?</font>

01:07:24.720 --> 01:07:26.720
Wallet's empty.

01:07:28.120 --> 01:07:30.360
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: So you've never seen him</font>
<font color="#ffff00">before.</font>

01:07:30.400 --> 01:07:32.320
<font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

01:07:32.360 --> 01:07:35.040
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know who he is.</font>

01:07:35.080 --> 01:07:37.400
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: His name was Liam Flynn.</font>

01:07:37.440 --> 01:07:42.160
<font color="#ffff00">He earned his living extorting money</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from businesses like yours.</font>

01:07:42.200 --> 01:07:43.640
<font color="#ffff00">Protection racket.</font>

01:07:43.680 --> 01:07:45.680
<font color="#ffff00">For a man called Eddie Nero.</font>

01:07:45.720 --> 01:07:47.800
<font color="#00ffff">I wouldn't know anything about that.</font>

01:07:47.840 --> 01:07:50.280
<font color="#00ffff">I told you what happened. That's it.</font>

01:07:51.600 --> 01:07:52.960
<font color="#ffff00">All right, Mr Gallo.</font>

01:07:53.960 --> 01:07:57.160
<font color="#ffff00">We'll have a quick word with your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">daughter and we'll be on our way.</font>

01:07:57.200 --> 01:07:59.600
<font color="#00ffff">She's got nothing to say</font>
<font color="#00ffff">more than what I've said.</font>

01:07:59.640 --> 01:08:02.240
<font color="#ffff00">Why don't we sit down, Miss Gallo?</font>

01:08:07.320 --> 01:08:09.960
Your name came up on a list of
cinema goers at the Roxy

01:08:10.000 --> 01:08:11.840
the night the organist died.

01:08:11.880 --> 01:08:16.000
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah. My night off. My boyfriend</font>
<font color="#00ff00">works there.</font>

01:08:16.040 --> 01:08:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">Who's your boyfriend?</font>

01:08:18.840 --> 01:08:21.439
<font color="#00ff00">Ken. Ken Bullings.</font>

01:08:21.479 --> 01:08:23.560
<font color="#00ff00">His grandad's the projectionist.</font>

01:08:24.600 --> 01:08:27.080
<font color="#00ff00">Dad doesn't like him, so don't say</font>
<font color="#00ff00">anything.</font>

01:08:27.120 --> 01:08:29.040
<font color="#00ff00">He'd only start creating.</font>

01:08:29.080 --> 01:08:32.040
<font color="#ffff00">Well, what the eye don't see...</font>

01:08:33.359 --> 01:08:36.319
<font color="#ffff00">But we'll need you to come clean</font>
<font color="#ffff00">about last night.</font>

01:08:36.359 --> 01:08:38.800
<font color="#ffff00">Your father was paying Flynn off,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">wasn't he?</font>

01:08:40.120 --> 01:08:42.040
<font color="#ffff00">For how long?</font>

01:08:42.080 --> 01:08:44.000
<font color="#00ff00">As long as I can remember.</font>

01:08:44.040 --> 01:08:47.279
Had anyone else been in,
trying to offer their services?

01:08:48.319 --> 01:08:50.720
<font color="#00ffff">(GALLO CLEARS HIS THROAT)</font>

01:08:50.760 --> 01:08:55.160
<font color="#00ffff">I think you should go now.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">We can help you, Mr Gallo.</font>

01:08:55.200 --> 01:08:58.720
Protect you from Nero.
<font color="#00ffff">No, you can't.</font>

01:08:58.760 --> 01:09:01.680
<font color="#00ffff">Go now. Please.</font>

01:09:11.000 --> 01:09:12.800
<font color="#ffff00">Liam Flynn.</font>

01:09:12.840 --> 01:09:14.760
<font color="#00ffff">What's it to do with me?</font>

01:09:14.800 --> 01:09:18.359
They've kept quiet, Gallo and his
daughter. In case you were wondering.

01:09:18.399 --> 01:09:20.720
That's how your protection
racket works, isn't it?

01:09:20.760 --> 01:09:22.680
People too afraid to speak
out.

01:09:22.720 --> 01:09:26.800
If anything happens to them, we'll
come after you with everything
we've got.

01:09:26.840 --> 01:09:28.840
<font color="#00ffff">I'm quaking.</font>

01:09:30.000 --> 01:09:32.880
<font color="#ffff00">It's not us you've got to worry</font>
<font color="#ffff00">about though, is it?</font>

01:09:32.920 --> 01:09:35.720
<font color="#ffff00">Two of your properties burnt out.</font>

01:09:35.760 --> 01:09:39.240
<font color="#ffff00">Now one of your arm-breakers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">draws the short straw.</font>

01:09:39.279 --> 01:09:41.920
<font color="#ffff00">I'd say someone's trying to turn you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">over.</font>

01:09:41.960 --> 01:09:43.640
<font color="#00ffff">I'd like to see 'em try.</font>

01:09:43.680 --> 01:09:45.800
Who wouldn't?

01:09:49.920 --> 01:09:52.040
<font color="#00ff00">The eyes were more deep set,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I think. </font><font color="#00ffff">Mm-hm?</font>

01:09:52.080 --> 01:09:54.520
<font color="#00ff00">But, apart from that...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">How about this?</font>

01:09:54.560 --> 01:09:56.560
<font color="#00ff00">Better, yeah. Yeah, that's better.</font>

01:10:01.400 --> 01:10:03.600
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Thursday's just given us a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">description</font>

01:10:03.640 --> 01:10:06.280
<font color="#00ffff">of the type that did the windows in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at the Advice Centre.</font>

01:10:06.320 --> 01:10:08.240
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

01:10:08.280 --> 01:10:11.480
<font color="#ffff00">Well, when you're done, if you've</font>
<font color="#ffff00">got a minute.</font>

01:10:11.520 --> 01:10:13.520
<font color="#00ff00">OK.</font>

01:10:17.840 --> 01:10:18.960
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

01:10:19.880 --> 01:10:21.560
(DOOR OPENS)

01:10:26.800 --> 01:10:30.920
<font color="#00ff00">So...?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I just wanted a word, that's all.</font>

01:10:30.960 --> 01:10:32.880
<font color="#ffff00">I haven't seen much of you lately.</font>

01:10:32.920 --> 01:10:34.840
<font color="#ffff00">You're all right, are you?</font>

01:10:34.880 --> 01:10:38.120
<font color="#00ff00">I think I'm out of a job,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but apart from that I'm OK.</font>

01:10:38.160 --> 01:10:42.120
<font color="#ffff00">You've been working at this Advice</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Centre? </font><font color="#00ff00">A few days a week.</font>

01:10:42.160 --> 01:10:44.200
<font color="#ffff00">Can't be much money in that.</font>

01:10:45.920 --> 01:10:48.560
<font color="#00ff00">There isn't, but I like it.</font>

01:10:48.600 --> 01:10:51.080
<font color="#ffff00">You might look in.</font>

01:10:51.120 --> 01:10:56.480
<font color="#ffff00">I know you've seen Carol, but</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your Uncle Charlie and your Aunt</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Paulette'd like to see you.</font>

01:10:56.520 --> 01:10:59.400
<font color="#ffff00">No need to worry about running into</font>
<font color="#ffff00">me, I'm at work.</font>

01:10:59.440 --> 01:11:01.000
<font color="#00ff00">It's not like that.</font>

01:11:01.040 --> 01:11:03.040
<font color="#ffff00">Isn't it?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">No.</font>

01:11:04.440 --> 01:11:06.240
<font color="#00ff00">I'm just finding my feet is all.</font>

01:11:06.280 --> 01:11:09.080
<font color="#ffff00">Charity work?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Just helping people.</font>

01:11:09.120 --> 01:11:10.800
<font color="#00ff00">Same as you.</font>

01:11:10.840 --> 01:11:13.040
<font color="#00ffff">Oh. Sorry, sir. I can come back.</font>

01:11:13.080 --> 01:11:15.360
<font color="#00ff00">No, Jim, it's all right. I was just</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on my way.</font>

01:11:15.400 --> 01:11:18.760
<font color="#00ffff">If you've a minute, sir, Mr Bright</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would like a word about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Flynn stabbing.</font>

01:11:18.800 --> 01:11:20.520
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

01:11:20.560 --> 01:11:22.480
(DOOR CLOSES)
<font color="#ffff00">Well.</font>

01:11:26.480 --> 01:11:29.600
<font color="#ffff00">You know where to find me if</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you need anything.</font>

01:11:33.200 --> 01:11:35.200
<font color="#ffff00">Mind how you go.</font>

01:11:35.880 --> 01:11:37.880
(DOOR OPENS)

01:11:41.200 --> 01:11:42.600
Oh!
<font color="#00ff00">Hello.</font>

01:11:42.640 --> 01:11:43.960
Hello.

01:11:44.000 --> 01:11:46.440
How are things?
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, you know.</font>

01:11:46.480 --> 01:11:48.200
Same as ever.

01:11:49.520 --> 01:11:52.280
<font color="#00ff00">You met Uncle Charlie, then.</font>

01:11:52.320 --> 01:11:54.240
<font color="#00ff00">What did you make of him?</font>

01:11:54.280 --> 01:11:55.760
(CHUCKLES)

01:11:55.800 --> 01:11:58.240
<font color="#00ff00">Carol's nice though.</font>

01:11:58.280 --> 01:12:01.200
<font color="#00ff00">Did you see her?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes. (CLEAR THROAT)</font>

01:12:01.240 --> 01:12:03.880
<font color="#00ff00">I haven't seen her for ages.</font>

01:12:03.920 --> 01:12:07.240
<font color="#00ff00">I was supposed to see her on</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Tuesday, but something came up.</font>

01:12:07.280 --> 01:12:09.280
<font color="#00ff00">How's she looking now?</font>

01:12:10.360 --> 01:12:12.920
Oh, I'm just the driver.

01:12:14.200 --> 01:12:16.720
No time to socialise, just quick
hello, goodbye.

01:12:18.400 --> 01:12:19.640
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah.</font>

01:12:19.680 --> 01:12:21.680
<font color="#00ff00">I remember those.</font>

01:12:25.520 --> 01:12:28.640
<font color="#00ff00">Give her my love if you run into her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">before she goes back.</font>

01:12:28.680 --> 01:12:31.000
<font color="#00ff00">Don't expect I'll have time to see</font>
<font color="#00ff00">her now.</font>

01:12:31.040 --> 01:12:33.000
Really? You're busy?

01:12:33.040 --> 01:12:35.600
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah. Yeah. You?</font>

01:12:37.120 --> 01:12:38.760
Always.

01:12:39.960 --> 01:12:42.200
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I won't keep you from it.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">OK.</font>

01:12:42.240 --> 01:12:44.240
<font color="#00ff00">Bye.</font>

01:13:03.560 --> 01:13:06.760
That bit of business. I'm bringing
it forward.

01:13:06.800 --> 01:13:08.600
After hours.

01:13:08.640 --> 01:13:10.480
<font color="#00ffff">Is that wise?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Wise?</font>

01:13:10.520 --> 01:13:13.080
I've got the filth all over me
with Flynn's stabbing.

01:13:13.120 --> 01:13:15.040
I want it over.
<font color="#00ffff">But...</font>

01:13:15.080 --> 01:13:17.120
I'm not asking, I'm telling.

01:13:17.160 --> 01:13:19.000
<font color="#00ffff">When?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Tonight.</font>

01:13:56.840 --> 01:13:58.120
(LINE RINGS)

01:13:58.160 --> 01:14:02.440
Hello. Can you connect me to the
Peninsular and Oriental head
office, please?

01:14:31.000 --> 01:14:33.400
<font color="#ffff00">So, what couldn't wait?</font>

01:14:33.440 --> 01:14:36.680
The autograph book doesn't belong to
Leslie Garnier, sir. <font color="#ffff00">How's that?</font>

01:14:36.720 --> 01:14:38.640
Well, take a look at the autographs.

01:14:38.680 --> 01:14:42.200
The only one with a dedication to
Garnier is the last one,
from Valdemar.

01:14:42.240 --> 01:14:45.240
<font color="#ffff00">That's a pretty big conclusion to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">draw from not much.</font>

01:14:45.280 --> 01:14:47.520
There's something else.
You said it yourself.

01:14:47.560 --> 01:14:50.080
Laurel and Hardy were in England
in 1953.

01:14:50.120 --> 01:14:53.800
At that time, Garnier was aboard a
cruise ship, The Happy Wanderer.

01:14:53.840 --> 01:14:56.800
I've spoken to P&O, and on the night
of the 10th of February,

01:14:56.840 --> 01:14:58.320
it was anchored off Sydney.

01:14:58.360 --> 01:15:00.880
<font color="#00ffff">So...whose autograph book was it?</font>

01:15:00.920 --> 01:15:02.440
It's not Garnier's.

01:15:02.480 --> 01:15:04.960
I think with all of this Egyptiana:
the scarab,

01:15:05.000 --> 01:15:07.960
the fact that Beavis died
after watching The Pharaoh's Curse,

01:15:08.000 --> 01:15:10.000
I think somehow it's tied into
Valdemar.

01:15:10.040 --> 01:15:11.240
<font color="#00ffff">Valdemar?</font>

01:15:11.280 --> 01:15:14.240
Beavis steals the scarab
from the Pitt-Rivers Museum

01:15:14.280 --> 01:15:16.840
and meets whoever hired him
to hand it over at the cinema.

01:15:16.880 --> 01:15:19.520
Only, I don't think the killer had
any intention

01:15:19.560 --> 01:15:21.760
of leaving Beavis alive to expose
him.

01:15:21.800 --> 01:15:24.640
<font color="#ffff00">So he spikes his carton of orange</font>
<font color="#ffff00">juice.</font>

01:15:25.680 --> 01:15:27.240
<font color="#00ffff">How does he manage that?</font>

01:15:27.280 --> 01:15:29.280
<font color="#00ffff">The cartons are all sealed,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">aren't they?</font>

01:15:29.320 --> 01:15:33.160
<font color="#00ffff">If he's buying them off</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the usherette, all the cartons</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would have to be poisoned.</font>

01:15:33.200 --> 01:15:35.400
<font color="#00ffff">Else she's in on it.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Here, try one.</font>

01:15:35.440 --> 01:15:38.600
Go on. It's perfectly safe. Oh,
sorry. Take this.

01:15:43.120 --> 01:15:44.560
I just killed you.

01:15:44.600 --> 01:15:47.000
It's not in the juice.

01:15:47.040 --> 01:15:49.160
<font color="#ffff00">The poison was in the straw.</font>

01:15:49.200 --> 01:15:52.280
Garnier said Beavis was waiting for
someone in the private lounge.

01:15:52.320 --> 01:15:54.720
None of the staff remember selling
him a Whakahari.

01:15:54.760 --> 01:15:56.480
<font color="#00ffff">So how's he come by it, then?</font>

01:15:56.520 --> 01:15:59.400
Once the film was started,
all eyes are on the screen.

01:15:59.440 --> 01:16:02.560
So whoever's buying the scarab
can slip into the cinema in the dark,

01:16:02.600 --> 01:16:05.560
take the seat next to Beavis,
hand him a carton of squash

01:16:05.600 --> 01:16:08.000
and a straw laced with strychnine.

01:16:08.040 --> 01:16:11.240
<font color="#00ffff">Member of staff, then. If they've</font>
<font color="#00ffff">access to the refreshment stall.</font>

01:16:11.280 --> 01:16:13.880
See, we were never meant to look
into Beavis's death.

01:16:13.920 --> 01:16:16.000
A nobody, without a friend in the
world,

01:16:16.040 --> 01:16:18.520
who died supposedly of natural causes
at home.

01:16:18.560 --> 01:16:23.360
I think it's about Valdemar.
He's the original intended victim.

01:16:23.400 --> 01:16:26.560
<font color="#00ffff">How do you mean?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Garnier was never meant to die,</font>

01:16:26.600 --> 01:16:30.480
but once we came around asking
questions about Beavis,
I think he took it upon himself

01:16:30.520 --> 01:16:32.640
to make his own inquiries
before naming names.

01:16:32.680 --> 01:16:34.640
<font color="#ffff00">THURSDAY: You think he confronted</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the killer?</font>

01:16:34.680 --> 01:16:37.200
MORSE: I think he saw an opportunity
to make some money.

01:16:37.240 --> 01:16:41.080
To stop playing for peanuts
in some flea-pit cinema.

01:16:42.440 --> 01:16:44.720
Garnier saw Beavis hand over the
scarab.

01:16:44.760 --> 01:16:47.680
<font color="#ffff00">I thought he didn't see who was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Beavis.</font>

01:16:47.720 --> 01:16:50.040
He saw enough to know who it was.

01:16:50.080 --> 01:16:53.960
<font color="#00ffff">What could he have seen from up</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there? An arm? A sleeve?</font>

01:16:54.000 --> 01:16:57.240
Don't you think there's something
odd about this autograph book?

01:16:57.280 --> 01:17:01.840
Look, all of the signatures are
written across the narrow of the page

01:17:01.880 --> 01:17:03.960
rather than its length. And all
crammed in.

01:17:04.000 --> 01:17:05.960
All of them.
On the same side of the book.

01:17:06.000 --> 01:17:07.600
<font color="#00ffff">So?</font>

01:17:08.400 --> 01:17:10.400
<font color="#00ffff">Who holds a bloody book like that?</font>

01:17:12.640 --> 01:17:14.520
<font color="#ffff00">Someone who has to.</font>

01:17:15.720 --> 01:17:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">A man with only one hand.</font>

01:17:18.800 --> 01:17:20.920
And that's what Garnier saw from the
rooftop.

01:17:22.440 --> 01:17:25.760
<font color="#00ffff">STRANGE: The commissionaire? </font><font color="#ffffff">Well,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he'd worked the variety circuit.</font>

01:17:25.800 --> 01:17:27.720
Opened the door for all the greats.

01:17:27.760 --> 01:17:30.960
It's just another autograph book
stuck under the nose of a star

01:17:31.000 --> 01:17:33.320
who doesn't even see
who he's signing for anymore.

01:17:33.360 --> 01:17:36.720
<font color="#ffff00">So, what, Gordon adds Akhenaten's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">cartouche</font>

01:17:36.760 --> 01:17:39.760
<font color="#ffff00">and slips the book into Garnier's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">pocket before the performance?</font>

01:17:39.800 --> 01:17:42.120
<font color="#00ffff">STRANGE: Maybe he asked Garnier</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to mind it for him.</font>

01:17:42.160 --> 01:17:44.800
MORSE: Or he did it when he swapped
the Martini with a twist

01:17:44.840 --> 01:17:46.640
for the Martini with an olive.

01:17:46.680 --> 01:17:50.560
<font color="#00ffff">There you go.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Not a word to Mr De Vere.</font>

01:17:50.600 --> 01:17:52.640
<font color="#00ff00">I can keep a secret, Edmund.</font>

01:17:53.640 --> 01:17:55.520
<font color="#00ff00">So long as the price is right.</font>

01:17:55.560 --> 01:17:58.760
<font color="#00ffff">Why though? Where's the motive?</font>

01:17:58.800 --> 01:18:02.760
<font color="#00ffff">What possible link could there be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">between a Hollywood star</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and a one-armed doorman?</font>

01:18:02.800 --> 01:18:04.520
Actually, there is a connection.

01:18:04.560 --> 01:18:07.400
It's the same thing
they have in common with you, sir.

01:18:08.440 --> 01:18:09.680
<font color="#ffff00">Of course.</font>

01:18:09.720 --> 01:18:11.120
<font color="#00ffff">What?</font>

01:18:21.880 --> 01:18:23.280
Hello?

01:18:44.400 --> 01:18:47.120
(WHIRRING)

01:18:57.840 --> 01:19:01.280
<font color="#00ff00">You don't remember me, Mr Valdemar.</font>

01:19:01.320 --> 01:19:03.320
I'm afraid I don't.

01:19:03.360 --> 01:19:06.520
Should I?
<font color="#00ff00">No.</font>

01:19:06.560 --> 01:19:10.680
<font color="#00ff00">I suppose not, after 50 years.</font>

01:19:11.720 --> 01:19:14.280
<font color="#00ff00">But I remember you.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font>

01:19:14.320 --> 01:19:16.920
<font color="#00ff00">Second Lieutenant Roberts.</font>

01:19:18.240 --> 01:19:19.800
<font color="#00ff00">Private Gordon, sir.</font>

01:19:19.840 --> 01:19:22.040
<font color="#00ff00">Worcestershire Pals.</font>

01:19:22.080 --> 01:19:23.880
Good Lord.

01:19:23.920 --> 01:19:25.640
<font color="#00ff00">Coming back to you now, sir?</font>

01:19:27.440 --> 01:19:30.040
Nablus.
<font color="#00ff00">That's right, sir.</font>

01:19:30.080 --> 01:19:34.040
<font color="#00ff00">The advance to the Wadi al-Fara</font>
<font color="#00ff00">road.</font>

01:19:34.080 --> 01:19:39.560
<font color="#00ff00">You ordered our section to charge</font>
<font color="#00ff00">an Ottoman machine gun emplacement.</font>

01:19:39.600 --> 01:19:41.840
That was the order that came down
the line.

01:19:41.880 --> 01:19:44.520
<font color="#00ff00">No, sir.</font>

01:19:44.560 --> 01:19:48.640
<font color="#00ff00">The order that came down the line</font>
<font color="#00ff00">was to stand fast.</font>

01:19:49.720 --> 01:19:51.600
<font color="#00ff00">I found that out later.</font>

01:19:51.640 --> 01:19:54.680
<font color="#00ff00">The battle was already won.</font>

01:19:54.720 --> 01:19:58.880
<font color="#00ff00">But young Second Lieutenant Roberts</font>
<font color="#00ff00">hadn't got himself a medal.</font>

01:19:58.920 --> 01:20:01.560
<font color="#00ff00">And that wouldn't do.</font>

01:20:02.760 --> 01:20:04.760
<font color="#00ff00">Mowed down.</font>

01:20:05.840 --> 01:20:07.840
<font color="#00ff00">Our whole section.</font>

01:20:07.880 --> 01:20:10.520
<font color="#00ff00">My brother Ernie among them.</font>

01:20:10.560 --> 01:20:12.560
<font color="#00ff00">Cost him his life.</font>

01:20:12.600 --> 01:20:14.400
<font color="#00ff00">I was lucky.</font>

01:20:14.440 --> 01:20:17.440
<font color="#00ff00">Just an arm, and the hope of a life.</font>

01:20:17.480 --> 01:20:20.560
<font color="#00ff00">A normal man's life, leastways.</font>

01:20:20.600 --> 01:20:22.320
<font color="#00ff00">But we took that machine gun.</font>

01:20:22.360 --> 01:20:24.760
<font color="#00ff00">And you got your medal.</font>

01:20:25.760 --> 01:20:28.600
<font color="#00ff00">Course, by the time</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I was discharged from hospital,</font>

01:20:28.640 --> 01:20:30.920
<font color="#00ff00">the Armistice had been signed</font>

01:20:30.960 --> 01:20:34.800
<font color="#00ff00">and nobody was much interested</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in how a dozen men died</font>

01:20:34.840 --> 01:20:37.680
<font color="#00ff00">when the world was mourning</font>
<font color="#00ff00">17 million.</font>

01:20:40.560 --> 01:20:42.640
I was 19.

01:20:42.680 --> 01:20:45.320
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, I remember, sir.</font>

01:20:46.200 --> 01:20:48.280
<font color="#00ff00">Scarce old enough to shave.</font>

01:20:48.320 --> 01:20:50.520
<font color="#00ff00">But old enough to lie.</font>

01:20:51.920 --> 01:20:56.120
<font color="#00ff00">It was your report of the action</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that stood in the Regimental Record.</font>

01:20:56.160 --> 01:20:57.960
<font color="#00ff00">Made the papers, too.</font>

01:20:58.000 --> 01:21:02.560
<font color="#00ff00">How the brave, young Second</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Lieutenant won through.</font>

01:21:02.600 --> 01:21:06.000
No, no, no, no. No, that wasn't me.
That was the papers.

01:21:07.480 --> 01:21:10.640
The country needed heroes.

01:21:13.160 --> 01:21:15.120
(TYRES SCREECH)

01:21:22.480 --> 01:21:24.200
Come on.

01:21:24.240 --> 01:21:26.240
<font color="#00ff00">I tried to forget it.</font>

01:21:26.280 --> 01:21:28.280
<font color="#00ff00">That's the thing.</font>

01:21:28.320 --> 01:21:30.320
<font color="#00ff00">To put it all behind me.</font>

01:21:30.360 --> 01:21:35.440
<font color="#00ff00">And the only place, funnily enough,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that I could put it out of my mind</font>

01:21:35.480 --> 01:21:37.520
<font color="#00ff00">was at the pictures.</font>

01:21:38.920 --> 01:21:43.080
<font color="#00ff00">And then one day, there you were,</font>

01:21:43.120 --> 01:21:46.280
<font color="#00ff00">up on the screen, large as life.</font>

01:21:46.320 --> 01:21:47.640
<font color="#00ff00">Larger.</font>

01:21:47.680 --> 01:21:52.400
<font color="#00ff00">Only, you weren't Second Lieutenant</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Roberts any more,</font>

01:21:52.440 --> 01:21:55.640
<font color="#00ff00">you were Emil Valdemar,</font>

01:21:55.680 --> 01:21:59.120
<font color="#00ff00">star of The Pharaoh's Curse.</font>

01:21:59.160 --> 01:22:03.200
Smoke...
<font color="#00ff00">That'll be Mr De Vere, sir.</font>

01:22:03.240 --> 01:22:07.480
<font color="#00ff00">He's setting a fire to burn the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">place down so the owners'll sell.</font>

01:22:07.520 --> 01:22:09.440
<font color="#00ff00">It doesn't much matter now.</font>

01:22:13.400 --> 01:22:15.840
What do you want?
<font color="#00ff00">Justice.</font>

01:22:15.880 --> 01:22:17.320
<font color="#00ff00">For the boys.</font>

01:22:17.360 --> 01:22:22.320
<font color="#00ff00">After 50 years, an end to it for you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and me.</font>

01:22:23.440 --> 01:22:25.440
<font color="#00ff00">We should have gone with them.</font>

01:22:25.480 --> 01:22:27.480
<font color="#00ff00">Only, we didn't.</font>

01:22:27.520 --> 01:22:30.200
<font color="#00ff00">I can put that right now.</font>

01:22:32.280 --> 01:22:35.520
<font color="#00ff00">There's a piece of white cloth</font>
<font color="#00ff00">by the organ there, sir,</font>

01:22:35.560 --> 01:22:37.680
<font color="#00ff00">and a safety pin.</font>

01:22:37.720 --> 01:22:39.200
What?

01:22:39.240 --> 01:22:41.920
<font color="#00ff00">You remember what happened to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">cowards, sir.</font>

01:22:41.960 --> 01:22:44.920
<font color="#00ff00">Shot...at...dawn.</font>

01:22:44.960 --> 01:22:49.160
<font color="#00ff00">You pin it over your heart.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'll do no such thing.</font>

01:22:49.200 --> 01:22:53.120
<font color="#00ff00">With or without, it's all the same</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to me.</font>

01:22:54.200 --> 01:22:57.000
<font color="#00ffff">Gordon! What the hell's going on?</font>

01:22:57.040 --> 01:22:58.240
(GUNSHOT)
<font color="#00ffff">Argh!</font>

01:23:13.400 --> 01:23:17.040
(COUGHS)

01:23:22.320 --> 01:23:23.800
<font color="#ffff00">(COUGHS)</font>

01:23:25.920 --> 01:23:28.040
<font color="#ffff00">Morse! Morse!</font>

01:23:30.520 --> 01:23:31.880
(LOCKED DOOR RATTLES)

01:23:35.240 --> 01:23:36.960
(SCREAMS)

01:23:37.000 --> 01:23:40.360
(BREATHLESSLY) He's coming. He's
coming! <font color="#ffff00">Follow me.</font>

01:23:43.480 --> 01:23:46.560
(COUGHS) Gordon.
<font color="#00ff00">Stay back!</font>

01:23:47.320 --> 01:23:48.440
Don't.

01:23:53.040 --> 01:23:54.840
Gordon! Come back! No!

01:24:22.160 --> 01:24:25.280
(GASPS FOR AIR)

01:24:31.760 --> 01:24:34.560
<font color="#ffff00">(THURSDAY COUGHS)</font>

01:24:34.600 --> 01:24:36.520
<font color="#ffff00">Come on.</font>

01:24:36.560 --> 01:24:38.560
(COUGHS)

01:24:50.920 --> 01:24:52.920
(COUGHING)

01:24:57.800 --> 01:24:59.800
(COUGHING)

01:24:59.840 --> 01:25:01.840
(APPROACHING SIRENS)

01:25:10.920 --> 01:25:12.920
<font color="#00ffff">STRANGE: Thanks very much, matey.</font>

01:25:16.160 --> 01:25:18.480
<font color="#00ffff">No survivors,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">according to the fire boys.</font>

01:25:24.360 --> 01:25:26.600
<font color="#00ff00">With De Vere gone,</font>

01:25:26.640 --> 01:25:29.040
<font color="#00ff00">we've no way to prove who put him up</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to setting the fire.</font>

01:25:29.080 --> 01:25:31.080
<font color="#ffff00">No way to prove it maybe, sir.</font>

01:25:31.120 --> 01:25:33.840
<font color="#ffff00">But Eddie Nero's very close</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with the owner's son.</font>

01:25:33.880 --> 01:25:36.000
<font color="#00ff00">He was for selling the place,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">wasn't he?</font>

01:25:37.000 --> 01:25:39.640
<font color="#00ff00">I suppose there's nothing to stop it</font>
<font color="#00ff00">being developed now.</font>

01:25:39.680 --> 01:25:42.160
<font color="#ffff00">We'll get Nero, sir, sooner or</font>
<font color="#ffff00">later. </font><font color="#00ff00">Will we?</font>

01:25:43.720 --> 01:25:47.400
<font color="#00ff00">Division's eye turned upon Thames</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Valley? This race business?</font>

01:25:47.440 --> 01:25:50.840
<font color="#00ff00">Now one of Nero's racketeers</font>
<font color="#00ff00">stabbed to death in the street?</font>

01:25:52.320 --> 01:25:54.000
<font color="#00ff00">It bodes ill, Thursday.</font>

01:25:55.400 --> 01:25:57.400
<font color="#ffff00">We're still on the job, sir.</font>

01:25:58.520 --> 01:26:00.640
<font color="#00ff00">I fear this time it might not be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">enough.</font>

01:26:02.400 --> 01:26:06.560
<font color="#00ff00">"Except the Lord keep the city,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Watchman waketh but in vain."</font>

01:26:08.960 --> 01:26:11.320
<font color="#ffff00">Listen...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">No, no. On your way now.</font>

01:26:11.360 --> 01:26:13.720
Don't want to hit the rush hour.

01:26:15.520 --> 01:26:17.840
<font color="#ffff00">You're the best of us, Fred.</font>

01:26:20.520 --> 01:26:22.440
The best of us never came home.

01:26:37.520 --> 01:26:38.720
(ENGINE STARTS)

01:26:40.280 --> 01:26:42.680
<font color="#ffff00">Bye!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Bye-bye.</font>

01:26:42.720 --> 01:26:45.200
<font color="#00ffff">Take care. See you soon.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Bye.</font>

01:26:47.240 --> 01:26:50.120
(BLAST OF "DIXIE" ON CAR HORN)

01:26:51.320 --> 01:26:53.800
<font color="#00ff00">Well, that's that, then.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yeah.</font>

01:26:53.840 --> 01:26:55.400
That's that.

01:27:00.400 --> 01:27:02.560
<font color="#00ff00">You do not need it for evidence?</font>

01:27:02.600 --> 01:27:05.320
<font color="#ffff00">There's no case to take to court,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Doctor.</font>

01:27:05.360 --> 01:27:07.360
<font color="#ffff00">It's back where it belongs.</font>

01:27:08.360 --> 01:27:10.360
<font color="#00ff00">The man who did these things,</font>

01:27:10.400 --> 01:27:12.880
<font color="#00ff00">in the final judgement...</font>

01:27:14.080 --> 01:27:16.440
<font color="#00ff00">..did his heart speak against him,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">do you think?</font>

01:27:16.480 --> 01:27:18.920
<font color="#ffff00">Gordon? Who knows?</font>

01:27:20.120 --> 01:27:21.320
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not one for all that.</font>

01:27:21.360 --> 01:27:23.920
<font color="#00ff00">And the afterlife?</font>

01:27:23.960 --> 01:27:25.960
<font color="#ffff00">Lies beyond our jurisdiction.</font>

01:27:28.440 --> 01:27:30.560
<font color="#00ff00">The detective and the archaeologist.</font>

01:27:30.600 --> 01:27:33.600
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps we're not so very different</font>
<font color="#00ff00">after all.</font>

01:27:34.800 --> 01:27:38.160
How's that?
<font color="#00ff00">We both speak for those who cannot.</font>

01:27:38.200 --> 01:27:42.280
<font color="#00ff00">You with your fingerprints,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and me with my fragments of pottery.</font>

01:27:43.280 --> 01:27:47.120
<font color="#00ff00">We are, each of us, I think, keepers</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of the dead.</font>

01:27:52.520 --> 01:27:55.280
How does someone start a policeman
and end up a thief?

01:27:56.600 --> 01:27:57.760
<font color="#ffff00">Beavis, you mean?</font>

01:27:58.920 --> 01:28:02.040
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you know as well as I do,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that given the right circumstances,</font>

01:28:02.080 --> 01:28:04.160
<font color="#ffff00">anybody's capable of anything.</font>

01:28:05.160 --> 01:28:07.960
<font color="#ffff00">Plus, he had no family</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to keep him on the straight.</font>

01:28:08.000 --> 01:28:09.960
<font color="#ffff00">Lot to be said for family.</font>

01:28:10.000 --> 01:28:12.000
And what if you don't have any?

01:28:13.360 --> 01:28:15.440
Do you think that's how you end up
your days?

01:28:15.480 --> 01:28:20.040
Alone in some two-bob kip,
nothing but a bottle for company?

01:28:20.080 --> 01:28:23.200
<font color="#ffff00">That's his future, not yours.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You'll make better choices.</font>

01:28:24.720 --> 01:28:29.200
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, Carol said to say, er, cheerio,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">by the way.</font>

01:28:29.240 --> 01:28:32.280
They've gone back, then?
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

01:28:33.280 --> 01:28:35.120
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah, they've gone back.</font>

01:28:35.160 --> 01:28:37.560
<font color="#ffff00">Good of you to show her around.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Don't mention it.</font>

